Umubare w'abanduye icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, uri kwiyongera cyane hagati ya 1 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Umubare w'abanduye Coronavirus (COVID-19) ugereranywa n'uw'abanduye mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EEA) n'uw'u Bwongereza, byemeza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje kwiyongera mu bihugu byose, nubwo kigenda gitandukana bitewe n'ibihugu.
Ishingiye ku byaranze Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo nderabuzima by'indembe bigomba kongera uburyo bwo kwitegura umubare wiyongereye w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho by'umwihariko mu buryo bufite ubushobozi buhambaye.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, habonetse icyorezo cy'indwara ya Pneumonia y'ubwoko butazwi.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara mu Bushinwa cyatangaje ko hari coronavirus nshya, ubu yitwa SARS-CoV-2, ari yo iteza indwara.
Kubera ko indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2, yahawe izina ry'indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibihamya bigaragaza ko 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 bafite indwara ziterwa n'ubuhumekero, yaba ifitanye isano na nimononiya cyangwa idafitanye isano na yo, kandi abenshi muri bo barakize.
Mu byiciro 14 bya COVID-19 usanga ari indwara ikomeye cyane, bisaba kujya mu bitaro, mu gihe mu bice 6% bikurikira, indwara iba ikomeye cyane, ikaba ikeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bwimbitse.
Imibare y'abapfuye mu bitaro bishwe na COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye imiterere y'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cyo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka Burayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza, tukayigereranya n'intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Nanone kandi, twagereranyije imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'u Bushinwa, COVID-19 yongeye gukwirakwira mu karere, kandi imibare y'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi ubu irakurikirana uko iki gihugu kimeze.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu kinyamakuru cyitwa Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. cyasohotse ku itariki ya 5 Werurwe, hatangajwe ko ari bwo bwa mbere mu Burayi hagize umuntu wa mbere wafashwe na COVID-19 nk'uko byemezwa na OMS.
Mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA, u Bufaransa bwamenyesheje ku wa 24 Mutarama 2020 ko bwabonye abantu batatu ba mbere bagaragaye baturuka i Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, ibihugu byose 30 bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza (UK) byari bimaze kubona abarwayi ba COVID-19, aho ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 habonetse abarwayi 39,768 n'abapfuye 1727 harimo 17,750 n'abapfuye 1,441 mu Butaliyani honyine.
Kubona umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 hamwe n'ibyabaye
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) cyandika amakuru y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 ku isi hose, kandi buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo, hakoreshejwe uburyo bwemewe n'amategeko, nk'ubw'ubushikiranganji bw'ubuzima bw'ibihugu, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'iz'akarere, n'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS).
Aya makuru akoreshwa mu gupima ubukana bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza no kubihuriza hamwe n'ubwandu bwo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'icyitegererezo cy'uburebure bw'abanduye COVID-19, twakoze ibarura ry'iminsi 14 y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19, dufata ingamba zo gukwirakwiza COVID-19 mu buryo busanzwe mu bihugu byose by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA n'Ubwongereza kuva ku wa 1 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone kandi, twatanze imibare y'ubwandu buri gihugu cyamenyeshejwe ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo, maze tugereranya n'ubwandu bwo mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Uko COVID-19 yagenze mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Imibare yose y'ibanze y'iminsi 14 ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, ni kimwe n'ibyavuzwe mu ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange, umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 watangiye kwiyongera ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma wiyongera cyane kugeza ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020.
Ibi byibanze ku kwiyongera kw'abatangajwe ko banduye muri Italy, ariko mu bindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, habonetse umubare wiyongera w'abanduye COVID-19 (Ibikoresho by'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, ugereranyije n'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku wa 31 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020.
Yashimangiye ko mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bitatu cyangwa bitarenga, saa munani z'igitondo ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, mu bindi bihugu 15 bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, hari hamaze kuboneka umubare w'abanduye wahuye n'uw'abanduye mu Butaliyani.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu bigaragaza ko imibare y'abandura COVID-19 iri kwiyongera cyane mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka Buraya (EU/EEA) n'Ubwongereza.
Imiterere y'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 byerekana ko icyorezo gikomeje kwiyongera mu bihugu byose.
Byongeye kandi, kubera ko ibihugu bitandukanye biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, itandukaniro hagati y'ibisubizo by'ubuzima rusange bw'igihugu, hamwe n'ibisobanuro by'ibyorezo bitandukanye mu bihugu bitandukanye, hamwe na protocole zitandukanye zo guhitamo abarwayi, birakenewe kugirango COVID-19 yemezwe, harimo no gupima gufata.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu bice by'u Butaliyani byibasiwe n'icyorezo bavuze ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi bw'indembe, kandi amakuru aturuka mu bitangazamakuru agaragaza ko ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe byo muri utwo turere byamaze kugera ku bushobozi bwuzuye.
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 ubu iraboneka ku rwego rwa EU/EEA ku bipimo bya 6% na 1% by'abanduye gusa (amakuru ntabwo agaragara).
Ariko kandi, bagomba gukusanya amakuru y'ubugenzuzi mu buryo bufite gahunda, bwibanda ku mubare w'abanduye n'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bwagaragaje ko umubare w'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze n'ibisanzwe mu Burayi, ari 29.2 mu Budage ku baturage 100,000, naho 4.2 muri Portugal.
Ibi bivuze ko ibindi bihugu bifite umutungo muto cyangwa munini kurusha u Butaliyani (ibitanda 12.5 by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe n'ubuvuzi bw'ingutu ku baturage 100,000 mu 2010-11).
Umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bitaro muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA na UK, ni urugero rw'imiterere y'uburwayi ifitanye isano n'ubwinshi bw'abarwayi, igaragaza ko uburwayi bufite > 90% by'abanduye barenze ubushobozi bw'ibitaro bya ICU, nk'uko byatanzwe mu isesengura rya gatandatu ry'igikorwa cy'ubugenzuzi bw'ibyago bya COVID-19 cyakozwe na ECDC.
Kubera ko abantu bakomeje kugaragara mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu bice bimwe by'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibigo nderabuzima bya ICU bigakira abaturage bo mu karere runaka, amakuru y'abantu bakomeje kugaragara mu bice by'Akarere n'amakuru y'ibigo nderabuzima bya ICU, byaba byiza biboneka mu bisobanuro by'ibigo by'Akarere ku kigero cya 2 (NUTS-2).
Ibyaranze Ubutaliyani n'imiterere iriho mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje gukwirakwira mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA ndetse no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo nderabuzima by'ingoboka bigomba kwitegura icyorezo cy'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 gikomeje gukwirakwira mu baturage, ndetse n'umubare wiyongera w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho by'umwihariko mu buvuzi bw'ingoboka, nk'uko byagenze mu bice by'u Butaliyani byibasiwe n'iki cyorezo.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'igenzura ry'ibyago byihuse rya ECDC, uburyo bwihuse, bwihuse kandi burambuye bwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 burakenewe aho gutuma ikwirakwira ryayo ritinda, kuko niba itashyizwe mu bikorwa hakiri kare, ukwiyongera kwitezwe mu buryo bwihuse kw'imanza nk'izi ntikuzatuma abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro bibasha kumenya, kwemera no guhuza ibisubizo byabo.
Ibipimo byihuse by'ibyago byo guhangana n'icyorezo byashyizwe ku rutonde rw'ingamba zo kwita ku buzima rusange.
Hari igihe gito cy'amahirwe, aho ibihugu bishobora kongera imbaraga mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya igitutu ku buzima.
Iyo ibyo bitagenze neza, birashoboka ko inzego z'ubuzima mu bindi bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Umuryango w'Abibumbye (EEA) zishobora guhura n'ikibazo cy'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi bakeneye ubuvuzi bw'indembe mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) cyatewe na SARS-CoV-2 kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3000, kandi cyanduza abarenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu ku isi, kikaba ari icyorezo ku bantu.
Kimwe na SARS-CoV, virusi ifitanye isano na yo yatumye abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi barwara SARS mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba yaranduriye mu bibugu kandi igaragaza ibimenyetso nk'ibyo.
Ariko COVID-19 ifite ubukana buciriritse n'ubwandu buciriritse kurusha SARS, ariko ifite ubwandu bwinshi kandi igera ku bantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko, ndetse igera no ku bagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza umubare wiyongereye w'ibitabo ku ndwara zikomeje kugaragara, iyi nyandiko igerageza gutanga isuzuma rikwiye kandi rirambuye ry'ikibazo cy'ubushakashatsi kirimo kigenda gikura.
Twakurikije ibintu by'ibanze biranga indwara ziterwa n'ibyorezo, indwara ziterwa n'imiti, indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu, uburyo bwo kuzisuzuma, kuzirwanya, kuzirwanya no kuzirwanya.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko iyi nama izadufasha gusobanukirwa no kurwanya iyi ndwara iteje akaga.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi wo ku wa 25 Mutarama 2020 wari udasanzwe kandi utazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu ngo zabo mu biruhuko byose no mu byumweru byinshi nyuma yaho kubera icyorezo gishya cy'indwara zandura.
Kubera ko virusi ya coronavirusi (CoV) ari yo yatumye habaho icyorezo cy'indwara ifata imyakura (SARS) mu 2003, ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS) wayise SARS-CoV-2 ndetse n'indwara ifitanye isano na yo wayise COVID-19.
Icyorezo cyatangiye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, gihita gikwira mu gihugu hose no mu bindi bihugu 50 byo ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yateye abantu 80,000 banduye COVID-19, abasaga 40,000 barakira, naho abagera ku 3,000 barapfa.
OMS yatanze umuburo ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa mbere w'abaturage" kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko tubikesha PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe cy'amezi abiri gusa hamaze gutangwa ubushakashatsi burenga 200 kuri COVID-19, bugaragaza virusi, icyorezo, icyorezo, uburyo bwo kuvura no kuvura, kuva haboneka umuntu wa mbere ku itariki ya 7 Mutarama 2020, aho hashyizweho icyiciro cy'ubwandu bw'icyorezo, uretse abarwayi batandukanye.
Iyi nama igerageza gusobanura neza iterambere ry'ubushakashatsi mu ngingo nshya kandi zikomeje gutera imbere.
Aho bishoboka, tuzakora ibishoboka byose kugira ngo tugereranye COVID-19 na SARS n'izindi ndwara ziterwa na CoV, nk'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, 2012).
Tuzasuzuma n'ibyo twize ku birebana no kwirinda indwara no kuzigaragaza, ndetse n'ibibazo byihutirwa ariko bikiriho.
CoVs zisanzwe zibonwa ko ari indwara zidakira abantu, ahanini zitera 15% by'indwara z'ibicurane.
Ariko muri iki kinyejana, twahuye n'izindi virusi ebyiri z'ubumara zica abantu, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatangiriye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, hanyuma zihita zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu zifite ubukana bukomeye n'ibipimo by'urupfu.
Bityo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa mu ishusho ya 1.1, ibinyabiziga by'indwara ya Pneumonia bitamenyekana inkomoko byatangiye kugaragara mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, hatangajwe ko icyemezo cya CoV cyatanzwe.
Ku itariki ya 15 Mutarama 2020, mu mujyi wa Wuhan, habaye umuntu wa mbere wahitanye abantu benshi.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu mijyi, intara n'ibihugu by'ibituranyi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, abashinzwe ubuzima batangaga amakuru y'ubwandu, agaragaza ko ushobora kwandura ku bantu.
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan wafashwe n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus, aho imodoka zose za Leta zahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bw'ubuvuzi ku ndwara bwagaragaje ko mu bantu 41 bemejwe ko banduye, 21 gusa ari bo bari bafite ibyangombwa by'ubuvuzi ku isoko ry'ibiribwa by'ibinyabuzima rya Wuhan, ryibonekeza nk'ikigo cy'ibanze cy'ubwandu buturuka ku nyamaswa zitamenyekana.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu ku isi.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yasohokaga, indwara yari imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bihugu 50 byo hirya no hino ku isi (Igishushanyo cya 2.2).
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda bihinduka vuba, imiterere n'uburemere by'iki cyorezo biracyari mu bibazo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ibigo byinshi bwerekeranye n'abarwayi 8,866 barimo 4,021 bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, bwatanze ishusho y'icyorezo ikurikira (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
