Bityo, kugira ngo umuntu abone uburuhukiro bw'ibimenyetso kandi arokore ubuzima bwe, uburyo bwo guhumeka bugomba gushyigikirwa, hakubiyemo imiti isanzwe yo guhumeka, umwuka wo guhumeka mu buryo bw'umwuka, umwuka wo guhumeka utanyuramo, n'umuyaga w'ubwubatsi utanyuramo, bitewe n'uburemere bw'uburwayi.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bikomeye by'ubuhumekero bagomba gushyigikirwa na Oxygénation de la membrane extracorporeelle (ECMO), ikoranabuhanga ry'ubuhumekero bw'umutima ryiyongereye rikoreshwa mu kuvura indwara z'umutima cyangwa ubuhumekero.
Muri rusange, gukomeza igipimo cya elegitoronike, gukumira kwandura kwa kabiri no gufatwa na septic shock, hamwe no kuvura, kurinda imikorere y'ingingo z'ingenzi, nabyo ni ingenzi ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2.
Byamenyekanye ko mu barwayi ba SARS na MERS, hari ibindi bikorwa by'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bigira ingaruka ku cyorezo cya sitokina.
Igitero cya sitokina ni uburyo bwo gutanga amakuru mu buryo bwa sisitemu, bugaragazwa no kurekura urutonde rw'ibikoresho birimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, na MCP-1.
Izi cytokines zituma ingirabuzimafatizo z'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri zisohora umubare munini w'ibinyabuzima by'ubwigenge, bikaba ari byo bituma habaho indwara ya ARDS n'izindi ndwara ziterwa n'imikorere mibi y'umubiri.
Immunosuppression ni ingenzi mu kuvura ibihuha bya sitokine, cyane cyane mu barwayi bakomeye.
Anti-IL6 monoclonal antibody corticosteroids na tosilizumab zikoreshwa mu kuvura cytocin storm.
Ubundi buryo bwo kuvura cytocin storm harimo kuvura indwara ziterwa n'imikorere y'umubiri w'ingirabuzimafatizo, IFN-Y, IL-1 na TNF, JAK, blintumomab, cytokine signaling 4 inhibitors na HDAC inhibitors.
Steroids zikoreshwa cyane mu kuvura SARS mu buryo bwo kuvura indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu.
Ariko, imiti ya Steroids yo mu rwego rwo hejuru ntiyari ifite akamaro mu kuvura indwara zikomeye z'ibihaha mu barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19.
Ahubwo bishobora guteza ingaruka zikomeye cyane cyane indwara y'imitsi y'amaraso, ishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku buryo umuntu atabasha kuyirwara.
Icyakora, imiti ya kortikosteroides yo mu rwego rwo hasi kugeza ku rugero ruciriritse, irasabwa gukoreshwa mu buryo bwitondewe ku barwayi ba COVID-19 barwaye cyane.
Mu gihe nandikaga iyi nkuru, nta muti wa virusi ukora neza wari umaze kumenyekana.
Ariko, umurwayi wo muri Amerika wahuye na COVID-19 yahawe umuti wa Remdesivir mu mitsi, kandi byagaragaye ko ugira ingaruka nziza.
Remdecivir ni umuti udasanzwe wa virusi, watangijwe na GILID mu kuvura indwara ziterwa na Ebola na Marlburg.
Nyuma, Remdesivir yagaragaje ko ishobora guhagarika izindi virusi ziterwa na RNA imwe, harimo virusi za MERS na SARS.
Ku bw'ibyo, Jilid yatanze ibi bikoresho mu Bushinwa kugira ngo bikoreshwe mu gupima abarwayi bafite SARS-CoV-2, kandi ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko ari byiza.
Byongeye kandi, baricytnb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir, na ribavirin byashyizweho nk'imiti ishobora gukoreshwa mu barwayi bafite ibimenyetso bikomeye byo guhumeka.
Gufata Lopinavir/Ritonavir mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi bishobora gutera gucibwamwo, gusinda, kuribwa, gukomereka kw'impyiko n'ibindi.
Ingaruka z'iyi miti ku zindi zikoreshwa mu barwayi zikwiye gukurikiranwa cyane.
Gukora plasma n'umubiri wa antikorupora mu barwayi bakize
Hari amateka maremare y'ibyagiye bikorwa mu gukusanya amaraso y'abarwayi bakize indwara zandura, kugira ngo bavurwe n'abarwayi bafite izo ndwara cyangwa se kugira ngo abantu bafite amagara mazima birinde kwandura.
Ni iby'ukuri ko abarwayi bakize baba bafite udukoko twinshi tw'umubiri mu maraso yabo kurusha abarwayi bafite indwara.
Imiti irwanya indwara n'ibindi bintu by'amahanga ni immunoglobulines (IG) ikorwa n'uruhu rw'umubiri rwa B, kandi ifata molekile runaka mu ndwara ziterwa n'indwara, ikazirimbura.
Hashingiwe kuri ibi, ingirabuzimafatizo zakusanyijwe mu maraso y'abarwayi bakize COVID-19 ndetse n'abarwayi 10 barwaye cyane.
Ibimenyetso byabo byagiye bihinduka mu masaha 24, ndetse n'uburwayi n'umuvuduko w'amaraso byagabanutse, ndetse n'umwuka wa ogisijeni mu maraso byagiye bihinduka.
Ariko kandi, kugeza igihe hazaba hakozwe uburyo bwihariye bwo kuvura, hakenewe ko hakorwa ubushakashatsi no gusobanura uburyo bwo gukoresha ku bwinshi.
Ikindi kandi, hari ibintu bimwe na bimwe bishobora gutuma umuntu atakaza ingirabuzimafatizo, bigomba kwitabwaho cyane kugira ngo bibonere umuti.
Urugero, abaturwanya bashobora gutuma umubiri ugira imbaraga nyinshi zo kurwanya indwara, bigatuma habaho cytocin release syndrome, ishobora no kuba ari uburozi bwica.
Ubusanzwe, amaraso aba afite ibice bike by'umubiri bigomba gukoreshwa mu kuvura abarwayi barwaye cyane.
Kugira ngo dukemure icyorezo cyugarije isi, ni ngombwa ko twitoza gukora udukoko tw'ubwirinzi tw'umubiri mu buryo bwihuse.
Ni yo mpamvu ari ngombwa kandi byoroshye gutandukanya utwo turemangingo twa B mu barwayi barwaye, no kumenya kode z'imiterere zandikaho udukoko tw'umubiri tw'ubumara cyangwa gusuzuma udukoko tw'umubiri tw'ubumara tw'ubumara dukoreshwa mu kurwanya poroteyine z'ingenzi za virusi.
Muri ubwo buryo, dushobora kongera ingano y'abaturwanya vuba cyane.
Mu Bushinwa, TCM imaze imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi ikoreshwa mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye.
Ariko kandi, mu buryo bw'imitekerereze ya TCM, ingaruka zayo ziva ku kuba hari ibintu bitandukanye bikubiye muri iryo funguro bifatanyije n'uburyo indwara yagaragajwe.
Ibyinshi mu bintu by'ingenzi bigize umubiri wacu ntibiramenyekana cyangwa ntibiramenyekana neza, kubera ko bigoye gutandukanya ibyo bintu cyangwa se ibibikorwamo.
Kubera ko nta muti wihariye cyangwa wihariye wa COVID-19 uboneka, TCM yabaye uburyo bwo kuvura bundi bushya ku barwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa abakize indwara zikomeye.
Urugero, Shu Feng Ji Du Capsules na Lian Hua King Wen Capsules byagaragaye ko ari ingirakamaro ku barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ibice bitandukanye by'Ubushinwa byakoresheje TCM mu kuvura COVID-19 byagize umubare munini w'abakize ku kigero cya 87% mu ntara za Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%) na Hunan (50%), mu gihe intara ya Hubei, aho TCM yakoreshejwe ku kigero cya 30% gusa mu barwayi ba COVID-19, yagaragaje umubare muto w'abakize ku kigero cya 13% mu ntara zose.
Ariko, iyi ni igereranya ridakwiriye kubera ko ibindi bintu bigira ingaruka, urugero nk'umubare w'abarwayi n'uburemere bwabo, bigomba gushyirwa mu byiciro.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Bole Zhang na bagenzi be basohoye inyigo igereranya imiti y'abirabura gusa (WM) n'ubuvuzi bw'ubumwe bwa WM na TCM.
Basanze igihe cyo kugarura ubushyuhe, gukira ibimenyetso no kujya mu bitaro ari gito cyane mu itsinda rya WM + TCM ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM gusa.
Icy'ingenzi cyane, ni uko ubwiyongere bw'ibimenyetso (kuva ku byoroheje kugeza ku bikomeye) bwari buke cyane mu itsinda rya WM+TCM ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM gusa (7.4% kuri 46.2%) kandi urupfu rwari ruto cyane mu itsinda rya WM+TCM ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM gusa (8.8% kuri 39%).
Icyakora, hakenewe ko ibizamini by'ubuziranenge byakozwe mu buryo bwagutse mu bigo byinshi kugira ngo TCM ikore neza kandi ibe ifite umutekano.
Gushyiraho uburyo bwo gukora no gusobanura ibice by'ubuvuzi bwa TCM cyangwa se ibishobora kubikorwamo, byaba ari ibintu bidasanzwe.
