Intambwe ya mbere yo kwirinda mu kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura ni ugukoresha udupfukamunwa; udupfukamunwa two kubaga n'udupfukamunwa two guhumeka N95 (umurongo wa 1860s) byombi bifasha mu gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Udupfukamunwa twa surgical tw'abantu bashobora kuba baranduye, tubabuza ko udutondo tw'amazi duca mu kirere tugera ku butaka bw'ibikoresho, bityo tukababuza kwanduza abandi.
Icyakora, udupfukamunwa twa N95 (Urutonde #1860) ni two twenyine dushobora guhagarika ubuhumekero bwa mikorobe kuva kuri 10 kugeza kuri 80 nm, aho 5% gusa ya virusi ishobora kwinjira mu buryo bwuzuye; SARS-CoV-2 ifite uburebure busa n'ubwa SARS-CoV, kandi zombi zifite uburebure bwa 85 nm.
Kubera ko utwo duce dushobora kwinjira mu bice bitanu by'ubwonko buri kimwe, abatanga serivisi z'ubuzima bahuye n'abarwayi bagomba kwambara N95 (Series # 1860) badafite udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi.
Uretse udupfukamunwa, abatanga serivisi z'ubuzima bagomba no kwambara imyenda y'igihumure ifashe mu gihe umuntu ari mu cyumba cyo kurinda virusi.
Virusi ishobora no kwandurira umuntu binyuze mu maso.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020, umuganga wambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95 yanduye SARS-CoV-2; birashoboka ko virusi yayinjiye mu mubiri we binyuze mu maso ye yabaga ashyushye.
Ku bw'ibyo, abavura bagomba gukoresha udupfukamunwa cyangwa udushumi tw'amaso mu gihe bakorana n'abarwayi.
