Abantu bafatwa nk'abafite intera y'ibirometero bitatu kugira ngo barinde umurwayi.
Ibi bikorwa byemejwe ko ari uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura no gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 ari virusi nshya mu bantu, yagombye kuba yarakaye cyane mu Bushinwa kubera ko ari SARS-CoV-X, nk'uko byatangajwe ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020.
Ariko, kugeza ku itariki ya 19 Mutarama 2020, umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Wuhan gishinzwe kurwanya indwara yabwiraga abantu ko virusi nshya itandura cyane kandi ko idashobora kongera kwiyongera hagati y'abantu, kandi ko kwirinda no kugenzura indwara bitagoye.
Ubwo butumwa bwagabanyije cyane ibyiyumvo byo kwitonda mu baturage, cyane cyane mu gihe igihugu cyose cyari cyiteguye kwizihiza Umunsi Mukuru w'Impeshyi, kandi igihe kinini cyo kugabanya ubwandu bwa Wuhan cyari cyaratakaye.
Inzego zishinzwe kurwanya indwara mu Bushinwa zishobora kuvana isomo kuri iyi nkuru ikaze kandi zikagira ibyo zihindura mu buryo bugaragara mu gihe kizaza.
Urugero, ibi bigo bigomba gufata ingamba zikurikira: (1) kwitonda cyane mu gutangaza itangazo rusange kuko ijambo ryose rigera ku baturage rifite agaciro kandi rishobora guhindura imyumvire n'imyanzuro; (2) kwita ku makuru adasanzwe mu bigo by'ubuvuzi nta gutegereza raporo zisanzwe z'abaganga cyangwa abaforomo; (3) gushyiraho ingamba nyinshi zo gukumira icyorezo mu gihe cy'intangiriro aho guhumuriza abaturage; (4) gukora imyitozo igamije guteza imbere ubumenyi bw'abaturage ku cyorezo no gupima no kuvugurura uburyo bwo gusubiza abaturage.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 yatangiye mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019.
Mu mezi abiri gusa nk'uko nandika iyi nkuru, yari imaze gukwira mu Bushinwa no mu bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo hirya no hino ku isi.
Kubera ko virusi ari SARS-CoV-Z kimwe n'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 na SARS, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatumye abantu bumva ko SARS yongeye kugaruka.
Ariko kandi, hari icyuho gikomeye hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, ari nacyo cy'ingenzi mu kugenzura icyorezo no kuvura abarwayi.
COVID-19 yibasira abagabo bakuze kurusha urubyiruko, n'abagore kurusha abagabo, kandi bafite ubukana bwinshi n'urupfu kurusha urubyiruko.
Imibare y'abahitanywe na SARS iruta iy'abahitanywe na COVID-19 (10.91% kuri 1.44%).
Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bashobora kwandura virusi nubwo baba badafite ibimenyetso, mu gihe SARS ishobora kuboneka mu gihe barwaye cyane, bigatuma COVID-19 igenda igorwa cyane kurusha SARS.
Ibi bisobanura impamvu SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira cyane kandi mu buryo bwagutse kurusha SARS-CoV.
Mu barwayi bamwe na bamwe ba COVID-19, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba ifite ingaruka mbi ku isuzuma rya RNA.
Ku rundi ruhande, abarwayi bakize bashobora kongera kwandura virusi.
Ibi byatangaje ko ibyagezweho byongereye cyane ibyago byo gukwirakwiza virusi.
