SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse he?
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 n'imbeba ebyiri zimeze nka SARS-CoVs zagize 96% by'ubumwe mu byerekeye imiterere y'ibinyabuzima, ntidushobora kwemeza ko SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse ku nyamaswa z'ibinyugunyugu.
Ni ikihe gikoko cyabaye ikinyabuzima cya mbere cyanduje virusi, ni ikibabi cyangwa ni umuntu?
Mu gihe tutazi ibisubizo bya mbere na kabiri, ntidushobora guhagarika neza ubwandu, kandi ntidushobora kongera guhangana n'icyorezo.
Nubwo ingamba zo gukora imideli n'iz'ibinyabuzima zagaragaje ko SARS-CoV-2 ifata ACE2, ni gute virusi yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso, hanyuma igakora impinduka mu buryo bw'ibipimo?
Ese virusi ishobora no gushyirwa mu bindi bice by'umubiri, ikagira ibice by'ingirabuzimafatizo zigize ACE-2?
Iyo tutabonye ibisubizo byumvikana by'ibyo bibazo, ntidushobora kubona uburyo bwihuse bwo kubashakisha no kubakiza neza.
Indwara izamara igihe kingana iki?
Ni gute virusi ikura mu buryo bw'ibinyabuzima mu gihe cy'ubwandu mu bantu?
Ese ni icyorezo cyugarije isi, kizarimbuka nka SARS, cyangwa kizakomeza kuza nk'ibicurane?
Ibi bibazo byose hamwe n'ibindi byinshi, bisaba ko tubisobanukirwa, ariko bishobora gufata igihe.
Ariko uko byagenda kose, nta kundi twabigenza uretse kugabanya ubukana bw'iki cyorezo vuba bishoboka, no gusubiza ubuzima bwacu mu buryo busanzwe.
