Imiterere y'ubwandu bwa coronavirus (CoV) n'ubw'abantu, byatangiye guhinduka mu myaka ibihumbi n'ibihumbi.
Mbere ya 2003, abantu babiri bavukaga kuri koronavirusi (HCoV) bari bazwiho guteza indwara z'uburwayi nk'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye (SARS) n'icy'indwara z'ubuhumekero zo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) byagaragaje ukuntu ubwandu bwa HCoV bushobora guteza akaga kandi bukanahitana.
Mu mpera za 2019, SARS-CoV-2 yongeye kugaragara mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, kandi yatangaje abantu benshi kubera uburyo ikwirakwira cyane, ariko ikaba yari ifite ubukana buke ugereranyije na SARS-CoV.
Kubera ko HCoV ari indwara yandurira mu nyamaswa, ni ngombwa ko tumenya inkomoko yayo.
Uduce twinshi tw'ubwandu bwa HCoV duturuka ku bibugu, aho usanga bidateza indwara.
Hari n'ibimonyo by'imbeba bizwi ko ari byo bihuza HCoV.
Gushyiraho ibimenyetso by'ibinyabuzima bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bantu mu kwirinda indwara.
Ubushakashatsi ku mikoranire ya COVID-Possida mu nyamaswa bushobora gutanga amakuru y'ingenzi ku cyorezo cya COVID mu bantu.
Muri iyi nama, turatanga isesengura ry'amakuru ariho ku ndwara zirimo HCoVs ndwi, yibanda ku mateka yazo yo kuvumburwa, ndetse n'inkomoko n'imikorere y'indwara ziterwa n'inyamaswa.
Icy'ingenzi ni uko tugereranya HCoVs zitandukanye, dukurikije uko virusi iterwa n'uburyo genome isubirwamo.
Muri iyi nama, hatangajwe ko hari byinshi byakozwe mu rwego rwo kurwanya icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Byongeye kandi, hakomeje kugarukwaho ko ari ngombwa guhindura poroteyine neza, kandi ko ingaruka z'ihindagurika ry'umugera ku burwayi ari nyinshi.
Coronavirus (CoV) ifitanye isano n'umuryango wa Coronaviridae, ugizwe n'itsinda ry'ubwandu bwa virusi za RNA imwe ifite uruhande rumwe, ifite ibimenyetso by'uko ari nziza.
Muri izo virusi za RNA, zirimo za virusi zifite ingirabuzima fatizo nini cyane z'imiterere iri hagati ya 26 na 32 za kilobase, zitwa COV kubera ko zigaragara nk'ikamba iyo zisuzumwe hakoreshejwe mikorosikopi ya elegitoroniki.
Mu buryo bw'ibanze, COVID ifite za genomes zitandukanyijwe zigira imiterere imwe.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu by'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima bigizwe n'ibinyabiziga bibiri binini by'ibanga (ORF1a na ORF1b), bihindurwa mu byiciro bya pp1a na pp1ab.
Polyproteins zikomeza gutunganywa zigakora ibice 16 by'ibinyabuzima bita "non-structural proteins" (NSP1-16).
Ibindi bice bigize genomine bigizwe na ORFs, ari byo poroteyine zigize imiterere y'umubiri, harimo spike (S), envelop (E), membrane (M) na nucleoproteins (N).
Hariho n'izindi poroteyine zifasha abantu mu buryo bwihariye, zikoreshwa n'abantu bo mu bwoko butandukanye bwa COVID.
Ukurikije urutonde rw'ibinyabuzima bitandukanye, COVID igabanyijemo ingero enye (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV), muri zo ingero ya beta-CoV ni yo igizwe na HCoV nyinshi kandi igabanyijemo ingero enye (A, B, C na D).
Ibimenyetso by'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima bigaragaza ko ibinyugunyugu n'imbeba ari byo bikomokaho cyane cyane alpha-CoV na beta-CoV, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zikomokaho cyane cyane gamma-CoV na delta-CoV.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka ibihumbi, COVID yakomeje guca mu cyiciro cy'ubwoko, ndetse hari n'izindi ndwara z'ingenzi ziterwa n'abantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana virusi zirimo abantu barindwi.
Muri byo harimo HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63, ari byo alpha-CoV.
Izindi beta-CoV eshanu zirimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, SARS-CoV, SARS-CoV-2 na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 byibanze ku bimenyetso byoroheje nk'ibicurane n'isukari.
Ku rundi ruhande, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 nshya ni zo ziterwa n'indwara nyinshi, zigatera indwara z'ubuhumekero mu barwayi benshi cyane bafite ibyago byo kurwara indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye (ARDS) n'iziterwa n'ubuhumekero.
Mu mwaka wa 1960, icyorezo cya mbere cya HCoV-229E, B814, cyatoranyijwe mu byuka byo mu mazuru y'abarwayi ba cyanko.
Kuva icyo gihe, ubumenyi bwinshi bwakozwe ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku mikorobe ya HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 igaragaza ibimenyetso by'ubwirinzi.
Icyakora, mbere y'uko icyorezo cya SARS kigera ku isi, abantu benshi bumvaga ko ubusanzwe HCoV nta cyo itwaye.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2003 ni kimwe mu byorezo byangije byinshi mu mateka y'iki gihe, aho cyibasiye abantu barenga 8.000 hamwe n'icyerekezo cy'uko 10% by'abanduye bapfuye.
Nyuma y'imyaka icumi, icyorezo cya Mares cyo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati cyatumye habaho icyorezo cy'indwara z'ibyorezo mu karere ka Arabiya, cyakwirakwira mu isi yose mu buryo bwihuse.
HCoV nshya yo mu 2019 (2019-nCoV), yaje kwitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni yo yatumye habaho icyorezo cya Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19), kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,120 no kwandura abantu barenga 91,000 kugeza ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Amatara y'akaga aracyavuza, kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Indwara zose uko ari 7 ziterwa n'inyamaswa, ni izo mu nyamaswa z'inkazi, mu nguge cyangwa mu nyamaswa zo mu ngo.
Ibimenyetso bitandukanye bishyigikira igitekerezo cy'uko imbeba ari zo zakomotseho, aho virusi zagiye zigira imiterere kandi zigaragaza ko hari itandukaniro ry'ibinyabuzima ritera indwara.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatanze imbogamizi zikomeye mu buvuzi, siyansi, imibereho n'umuco ku Bushinwa no ku isi.
Gukurikirana inkomoko y'indwara ziterwa n'inyamaswa za ACOV, bigaragaza amateka y'ibanze, imbaraga zituma habaho iyo mpinduka, n'ibikoresho by'ubutabazi by'ubwoko.
Ibi kandi bizatuma hagaragara cyangwa hagakorerwa ubushakashatsi ku byorezo bya SARS-CoV-2, bigahindura imikorere ya virusi, bigatuma habaho uburyo bwo guhagarika ikwirakwira ryayo mu gihe kizaza.
Muri iyi nama, dutanga isesengura ry'inkomoko y'indwara z'amatungo, ikwirakwira ry'ubwoko butandukanye n'imiterere y'indwara z'ubwandu bwa HCoV.
By'umwihariko: Turibanda ku ngingo zikurikira kandi tukaganira ku buryo virusi ya mbere ya HCoV idashobora gutera indwara mu bwoko bwayo bw'ibanze, ariko ikaza kuzana indwara mu bwoko bushya.
Nanone kandi, twasuzumye uburyo HCoV yateye imbere, aho iyo indwara zanduye zigenda zigabanuka, indwara zandura zigenda zigabanuka.
Ibiganiro byibanda ku ngaruka z'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kirimo kuba.
Kuva mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 30, abantu bari bazi ko inyamaswa zifite COVID.
Mbere y'uko HCoV-229E, B814 isohoka bwa mbere mu byuka byo mu mazuru y'abarwayi bafite imbeho, hari izindi virusi za COVID zatoranyijwe mu nyamaswa zitandukanye zanduye, harimo inkoko, imbeba, inka, ingurube, injangwe n'imbwa.
Mu myaka icumi ishize, hamaze kuvumburwa ubwoko burindwi bwa HCoV.
Igisobanuro cy'ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwa HCoV mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri (Igishushanyo cya 1) kizaba ari icy'ubumenyi kandi gitanga ibisobanuro.
Mu mwaka wa 1966, abantu batangiye kwandura indwara ya HCoV-229E bari barwaye indwara z'ubuhumekero bwo hejuru, maze batangira kubona uturemangingo tw'ibihaha twitwa WI-38.
Abanduye HCoV-229E bagaragaje ibimenyetso by'ibicurane birimo umutwe, gusakuza, gucibwamwo no guhekenya mu muhogo, ndetse n'ubushyuhe n'inkuba mu bantu bari hagati ya 10 na 20%.
Nyuma mu 1967, HCoV-OC43 yasobanutse mu buryo bw'ibanze mu buhinzi bw'ingingo mu nguge ntoya, nyuma yaho mu bwonko.
Ibimenyetso by'indwara ya HCoV-OC43 byerekanye ko ari kimwe n'iby'indwara ya HCoV-229E, idashobora gutandukanywa n'izindi ndwara z'ubuhumekero, urugero nk'ibicurane bya Influenza A na Rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 byombi byiganje ku isi hose, kandi byandura cyane cyane mu gihe cy'imbeho mu gihe cy'ubushyuhe buke.
Ubusanzwe, igihe cyo gukira k'iyi virusi zombi ni igihe kitageze ku cyumweru, nyuma y'ibyo hakaba hashize ibyumweru bibiri.
Ubushakashatsi bwakorewe ku bantu b'abakorerabushake bwagaragaje ko abantu bafite uburwayi butameze nabi banduye HCoV-229E, bakunze kugira imbeho yoroheje.
Abarwayi bake cyane bafite ubwirinzi butagendera ku matwara y'umubiri ni bo bagaragaza ko bafite indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero bwo hasi.
SARS, bita "atypical pneumonia", ni yo yari virusi ya mbere ya HCoV ikwirakwira ku isi yose mu mateka y'abantu, kandi SARS-CoV ni yo yari ifite impamvu, ni yo yari ya gatatu ya HCoV yavumbuwe.
Umurwayi wa mbere wa SARS yabonetse mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyatumye abantu 774 bapfa, hamwe n'abanduye 8,096 bakwirakwira mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane myinshi.
Hatitawe ku byanduza, hateganywa ko buri cyorezo gishobora gutera indwara ebyiri z'icyorezo, zikagira iminsi 4 kugeza ku minsi 7 yo gukira, kandi zikaba zigira ingaruka ku munsi wa 10 w'uburwayi.
Abandura SARS-CoV bashobora guhura n'imibabaro itangirana n'umubabaro wo mu mitsi, umutwe, umuriro, gucuha no guhinda umuriro, hanyuma bakagira guhumeka nabi, gucumba no guhumeka nabi.
Ubundi burwayi busanzwe bugaragazwa mu ma laboratwari ya SARS ni indwara z'ubwonko, ubwonko butameze neza, n'ubushishi bw'ibinyabutabire.
