Nubwo yavumbuwe mu Buholandi, yakwirakwiriye ku isi hose.
HCoV-NL63 igaragara ko ari yo iteza 4.7% by'indwara z'ubuhumekero, kandi iboneka cyane mu mpeshyi, mu itumba no mu itangira ry'itumba.
