Icyorezo cya kabiri cyabaye muri Koreya y'Epfo mu mwaka wa 2015, aho abantu 186 bemejwe ko banduye.
Ibimenyetso bya MERS ni kimwe n'ibya SARS, bigaragara mu cyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane.
Mu buryo bunyuranye na SARS, abenshi mu barwayi ba MERS bahura n'ikibazo cyo guhungabana kw'impyiko, ibintu bidasanzwe ku barwayi ba MERS mu ndwara ziterwa na HCoV.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero, urugero nk'ububyimba n'umunaniro, bari hejuru ya 30 ku ijana.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, hari hamaze kugaragara abantu barenga 2500 banduye MERS, ku kigero cya 34.4% by'abahitanwe na yo, bituma MERS-CoV iba imwe muri virusi zangiza cyane abantu bazi.
Kuva mu kwezi k'Ukuboza kugeza mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2019, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, hatangiye kugaragara abantu benshi bafite indwara ya pimiyobyabwenge ifitanye isano n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, OMS, ryemeje ko icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mpuzamahanga, ndetse ko ari icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, ku isi hose, abantu 90,053 ni bo bamaze kwandura, mu gihe abamaze gupfa ari 3.4%.
