SARS-CoV-2 itera indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zigaragazwa n'ubushyuhe, gucumba no guhumeka.
Bamwe mu barwayi bagaragaje ko bafite ikibazo cyo kuribwa cyane.
Pneumonia ni kimwe mu bimenyetso bikomeye cyane, kandi ishobora kwiyongera cyane mu buryo bwihuse, igatuma umuntu agira ububabare bukabije bwo guhumeka.
Nubwo SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 ari kimwe bitewe n'uko zifite urusobe rwinshi rw'imikorere ya nucleotide, ziri mu byiciro bitandukanye by'imiterere ya za virusi.
SARS-CoV-2 ni indwara nto cyane ariko ishobora kwandura cyane kurusha SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Hari abarwayi batagaragaza ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bashobora kuba baragize uruhare mu kwihuta kw'icyorezo ku isi hose.
Iyo SARS-CoV-2 igereranyijwe n'izindi virusi esheshatu za HCoV, igaragaza byinshi bihuriyeho n'ibindi bitandukanye.
Icya mbere, igihe cyo gukira n'igihe cyo kurwara HCoV ni kimwe.
Muri iyi ngingo, SARS-CoV-2 ikurikiza ingendo zisanzwe z'izindi HCoV esheshatu.
Icya kabiri, ubukana bw'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 buri hagati ya SARS-CoV na HCoVs zaturutse mu miryango ine (ni ukuvuga HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63).
Ku ruhande rumwe, SARS-CoV-2 igaragaza ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara mu gihe cy'ubwandu busanzwe bwa HCoV, harimo kuba idafite ibimenyetso, idafite ibimenyetso cyangwa idafite ibimenyetso.
Ku rundi ruhande, nubwo umubare w'abandura SARS-CoV uri hasi, hari umubare muto w'abandura COVID-19 bafite uburwayi bukomeye.
Icya gatatu, SARS-CoV-2 igaragaza uburyo bushishikaje bwo kwandura HCoV na SARS-CoV, byibasira abaturage.
Ku ruhande rumwe, SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo kwandura cyane nk'ubw'ubwandu bwa HCoV mu baturage.
