Kugira ngo dusobanukirwe neza ubuzima bwa COVID n'ibidukikije biyirinda, hakenewe ko inyamaswa z'ibinure zikomeza kugenzurwa, ibyo bikaba byatuma abantu batandura bakava mu nyamaswa bakajya mu bantu, bityo bikazafasha mu gukumira icyorezo mu gihe kizaza.
Mu gusoza, uburyo bwiza bwo gukumira virusi z'inyamaswa ni ukubuza abantu guhura n'aho virusi z'inyamaswa zaturuka.
Ibice byinshi by'ikibazo cy'inkomoko y'inyamaswa ya SARS-CoV-2 biracyari mu bwihisho.
Icya mbere, niba inyenzi zanduje virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 mu ngona, byaba byiza tubonye imimerere inyenzi n'ingona zisangiye mu bidukikije.
Icya kabiri, niba udukoko tugize uruhare rw'ibanze mu guhitana abantu, tugomba kumenya uko abantu bahura n'udukoko.
Icya gatatu, niba inyamaswa z'inshyimbo za gatatu ari zo zakoraga nk'abafasha mu kurera, byagombye gusobanuka neza uko zahuzaga n'inyamaswa z'amoko atandukanye, harimo abantu, inguge n'ingona.
Amaherezo, inyamaswa nyinshi zinyamaswa, harimo n'amatungo, zigomba kugenzurwa mu buryo bw'igerageza, kuko zishobora kuba zirashobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2.
Niba ari inguge, ingona cyangwa ikindi kinyamaswa, mu gihe kizaza, mu byaremwe by'ibanze, hashobora kuboneka SARS-CoV-2 isa n'iyo cyangwa virusi ya mbere.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeje muri iki gice buzatuma inzira y'ihindagurika rya SARS-CoV-2 mu nyamaswa isobanura byinshi mu gukumira no kugenzura COVID-19 mu bantu.
Ni ngombwa ko hashyirwaho amabwiriza mashya yo gusuzuma "abashidikanya ku cyorezo" na "abemejwe ko banduye" COVID-19.
Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryasohoye amabwiriza yihutirwa yo kugisha inama ku buvuzi bwa nikeleyeri bwo gusuzuma icyorezo cya 2019 novel coronavirus (2019-nCoV), kandi ayo mabwiriza ni ingirakamaro mu kurwanya icyorezo ku rwego rw'igihugu cyacu ndetse no ku isi hose.
Ariko kandi, Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara nshya. Ubumenyi bwacu n'ubumenyi bwacu bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro, bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa, ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abahanga mu buvuzi, bityo, uburyo bwo gupima no kuvura burimo gusubirwamo buri gihe.
Muri iyi baruwa, hari igitekerezo cyashyizwe hejuru ku mabwiriza yacu, kandi hashyizweho ibipimo bishya by'ubushakashatsi ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 (Icyiciro cya karindwi) "abashidikanyaho" n'"abemejwe" nk'uko byatanzwe na Komite y'Ubuzima y'Igihugu ya Repubulika ya Rubanda y'u Bushinwa.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, habaye icyorezo cyatewe na virusi ya 2019 ya coronavirus (2019-nCoV), cyiswe byemewe ko ari indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), maze iyi virusi yitwa SARS-CoV-2.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yashyize ahagaragara icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryakoze amabwiriza yihutirwa kandi yasohotse kuri interineti mu kinyamakuru cya Military Medical Research ku wa 06 Gashyantare 2020.
Kuva yasohoka, yagiye ituma abantu benshi bibaza.
Zirikana ko nubwo COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi bwacu n'ubumenyi bwacu bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro, bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'imikorere y'abaganga; bityo, uburyo bwo kuyirwara no kuyirwara bugenda buvugururwa buri gihe.
Urugero, ibitabo birindwi by'amabwiriza y'ubushakashatsi n'ubuvuzi ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 byasohotse mu nama y'ubuzima y'igihugu ya Repubulika ya Rubanda y'u Bushinwa (NHC) kuva ku itariki ya 16 Mutarama 2020 kugeza ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe 2020, byasohotse mu buryo buhuje n'ibisobanuro.
Ubu amabwiriza yacu yahawe ibitekerezo na Zhou et al. batanze ibitekerezo byoroshye bishingiye ku byo bize mu bitaro.
Ibikorwa byabo byongereye ibimenyetso bishya ku mabwiriza yacu, kandi byatanze ibisobanuro by'agaciro kuri iyi ndwara y'isi yose.
Turamushimira kandi tumushimira ku bw'umurimo we ukomeye.
Ariko kandi, ibikorwa byayo nabyo bikeneye kuvugururwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza agezweho yo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 (igerageza rya 7th edition) n'ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'Igitabo cya karindwi (3 Werurwe 2020), kugira ngo umuntu yemeze ko arwaye indwara runaka, agomba kuba afite ikintu kimwe mu bintu by'amateka y'indwara, kimwe n'ibindi bibiri mu bintu by'ubushakashatsi mu buvuzi, cyangwa se ibintu bitatu mu bintu by'ubushakashatsi mu buvuzi mu gihe nta mateka y'indwara bigaragara.
Amateka y'indwara: (1) mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu nkengero zawo, cyangwa mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso biboneka, mu karere kabamo abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu gihe cy'urugendo cyangwa igihe cyo kuba; (2) mu mateka y'abarwayi ba SARS-CoV-2 (harimo no gupima asidi ya nikeleyeri yemeza ko banduye); (3) mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu nkengero zawo, cyangwa mu yindi midugudu aho ibimenyetso by'indwara ya COVID-19 byibonekeye mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso biboneka; (4) mu mateka y'abarwayi bafite umuriro cyangwa uburwayi bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (urugero, mu mazu, mu biro, mu mashuri, mu byumba by'amashuri, n'ibindi), mu gihe cy'ibyumweru 2 harimo ubushyuhe/indwara ntoya yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ≥ 2 bikurikira.
Ibitangazamakuru: (1) ibimenyetso by'ubushyuhe n'/cyangwa guhumeka; (2) ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) umubare w'abatabazi b'amaraso mu gihe cy'ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze.
Gushakisha abemejwe ko banduye byashingiye ku bakekwaho indwara cyangwa se ku bimenyetso bya seriyo nk'uko byatanzwe haruguru: (1) gupima PCR y'igihe nyacyo kuri SARS-CoV-2 bigomba kuba ari byiza; (2) gukwirakwiza virusi yose igaragaza ko ifite ubushobozi bwo gukingira virusi nshya; (3) gupima SARS-CoV-2 mu cyiciro cya seriyo ku buryo bwihariye IgM na IgG; cyangwa guhindura IgG ya SARS-CoV-2 mu cyiciro cy'ubuvuzi, cyangwa se ku buryo bwihariye ≥4x.
Dushobora kubona ko ibipimo bya PCR by'igihe nyacyo by'indwara ya Aside ya nucleic mu mwuka cyangwa mu maraso byongerewe mu cyiciro cya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) no mu cya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020).
Gushyiraho ibimenyetso by'indwara mu bipimo by'amaraso byongewemo mu cyiciro cya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) no mu cya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); hanyuma mu cyiciro cya karindwi, hashyizwemo ibihamya bya serology.
Izo mpinduka zishingiye ku gikorwa cy'ubushakashatsi cyakozwe buri gihe, harimo gushakisha uburyo bwiza bwo kumenya aside ya nucleic muri iki gihe cyo kwihutisha gusuzuma, hamwe no gushyiramo amaraso y'igihumekero, byongereye uburyo bwo kubona ingero zitandukanye, kandi byongera imbaraga mu gutuma haboneka ingero z'indwara z'ubwoko bumwe mu buryo bwemejwe.
Uretse ibyo, hari ibimenyetso byinshi byatwibutsaga ko tugomba kwitonda mu gihe duhuye n'abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara z'uburwayi n'izindi ndwara z'uburwayi.
Bityo rero, Zhou et al. bagomba kuvugurura imiterere y'ibipimo by'imiterere y'umuntu, kuko basanze umuntu udafite ibimenyetso byo mu rwego rwa muganga ari "umuntu ufite ibyago bike".
Mu myitozo n'ubushakashatsi bukomeza, hakenewe kandi gusuzuma uburyo bwo kubara.
Mu gusoza, twizeye ko ibindi bimenyetso bifatika bizatangwa kugira ngo abasomyi batange ibitekerezo byabo.
Mu gusuzuma abantu bakekwaho ubwandu n'abamaze kubonerwa ibimenyetso, tugomba gukurikiza amabwiriza agezweho yo mu gihugu cye.
Kugira ngo dufashe, itsinda ryacu rizongera kuvugurura amabwiriza yacu mu gihe gikwiriye.
