Mu minsi ya nyuma y'ukwezi kwa mbere, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije gahunda y'ubukangurambaga, nyuma yaho Xi Jinping, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa, yavuze ko ari "intambara y'abaturage" yo kurwanya ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi.
Mu byo basobanuye ko ari "igihombo gikomeye mu mateka y'abantu", gahunda y'isuku yatangajwe ku ya 23 Mutarama, ihagarika ingendo zo mu mujyi wa Wuhan no hanze yaho, nyuma y'aho ikaba yaragutse igera mu mijyi 15 yo mu mujyi wa Hubei, igatuma abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 57 bahungabana.
Gukoresha imodoka bwite byari bibujijwe mu mujyi.
Imikino yo kwizihiza Umwaka Mushya w'Abashinwa (itariki 25 Mutarama) yahagaritswe mu bice byinshi.
Abayobozi batangaje ko hari hagiye kubakwa ibitaro by'agateganyo byitwa Hushenshan Hospital, byuzuye mu minsi 10.
Hakorewe indi bitaro, yitwa Lyshenshan Hospital, kugira ngo haboneke abarwayi benshi.
Usibye ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bibuga by'i Wuhan nk'ibigo by'inama n'ibibuga by'imikino, mu bitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yafashe izindi ngamba zo kugabanya icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutangaza ubuzima bwiza ku banyamahanga no kongera iminsi mikuru y'impeshyi.
Amashuri n'amashuri muri icyo gihugu byafunzwe.
Mu karere ka Hong Kong na Macau, ingamba nyinshi zafashwe, cyane cyane ku mashuri na za kaminuza.
Ibikorwa bya kure byatangijwe mu bice byinshi by'Ubushinwa.
Ingendo zo mu mujyi wa Hubei no hanze yazo zahagaritswe.
Imyiteguro y'urugendo rwa rusange yarahindutse, kandi amazu ndangamurage yose yo mu Bushinwa yafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Imihanda ya rusange yafatiwe mu migi myinshi, kandi abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bashyizwe mu myigaragambyo yo hanze. Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, igihe icyorezo cyageraga ku isi hose, abategetsi b'Abashinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kubuza virusi kuva mu bindi bihugu igataha mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Beijing yategetse ko abagenzi mpuzamahanga bose baza mu mujyi bagomba kumara iminsi 14 mu kato. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, mu Bushinwa, hari umuntu umwe gusa wanduye mu gace ke mu minsi itanu ishize, wari uvuye i Istanbul ajya i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Li Keqiang, umukuru w'u Bushinwa, yatangaje ko ubwandu bwo mu karere buhagaze, kandi ko icyorezo cyahagaritswe mu Bushinwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, mu mujyi wa Hubei, uretse Wuhan, hongeye gufungurwa ingendo nyuma y'amezi abiri hashyizweho gahunda yo gufunga. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko ubwenegihugu bw'abafite viza cyangwa ibyangombwa byo gutura mu gihugu cyabo buzahagarikwa nyuma ya 28 Werurwe, kandi ntiyatangaje igihe uwo muteguro uzarangirira.
Abashaka kujya mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba muri ambasade cyangwa mu biro by'u Bushinwa.
Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yashishikarije abantu kongera gutangira ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi n'inganda ku wa 30 Werurwe, ndetse itanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku nganda. Komite ya Leta yatangaje ko mu gihugu hose ku wa 4 Mata saa kumi za mu gitondo, umunsi wo gupfusha uzatangira ku isaha ya saa tatu, mu gihe hazabaho iminota itatu yo kwicecekera.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020, hemejwe ko COVID-19 yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo iturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare habonetse ubwandu bwinshi, ibi bikaba byatewe ahanini n'ikoraniro ry'idini rishya ryitwa Shincheonji Church of Jesus, riri i Daegu.
Abantu benshi bakeka ko icyateye iyo ndwara ari abantu basengaga Shincheonji, bari baje gusura umujyi wa Wuhan Degu.
Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, 1261 mu bayoboke 9336 b'iryo dini, ni ukuvuga 13% by'abayoboke bose, bari bafite ibimenyetso.
Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, Koreya yari imaze kubona abarwayi barenga 2000, ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare bari bamaze kugera kuri 3150.
Nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu ba Koreya y'Epfo basuzumwe bagasanga banduye virusi, ibiro bya gisirikare byose byo muri Koreya y'Epfo byatangiye gufungirwa mu kato.
Ibi byagize ingaruka no ku ngengabihe y'indege, kuko Koreya y'Epfo yatangije gahunda nini kandi iteganijwe cyane ku isi yo gupima abantu benshi, gutandukanya abantu banduye, kubakurikirana, no gutandukanya abo bahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gupima harimo kwandikisha ibimenyetso by'abimukira kuri porogaramu za terefone, gupima virusi mu modoka, ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima ku buryo abantu 20,000 bashobora gupimwa buri munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo, izwiho kuba yaragize icyo igeraho mu kugabanya icyorezo, ariko ntikibe mu mijyi yose, yatangiye mu rwego rwo gusubiza ikibazo cya Perezida Moon Jae-in, cyatumye abaturage bo muri Koreya y'Epfo bagira imyumvire itandukanye ku byerekeye imimerere.
Abaturage benshi bo muri Koreya bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zo gushimira Moon cyangwa kumushinja ko yafashwe nabi n'ubutegetsi.
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, umubare muto w'abanduye mu cyumweru kimwe mu byumweru bine, wabaye tariki ya 23 Werurwe.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abimukira bose bazaba bari mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Amakuru yo ku ya 1 Mata agaragaza ko Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ubutumire bw'ibihugu 121 byo gufasha mu igerageza ry'iyi virusi.
Irani yatangaje ku wa 19 Gashyantare, ko hari abantu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye SARS-CoV-2 mu gihugu cya Comm, aho nyuma yaho uwo munsi hapfuye umuntu umwe nk'uko bitangazwa na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi.
Mu byo Leta yari yabanje gutangaza harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'indi mihango y'umuco, imikino n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, gufunga za kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yashyizeho miliyari 5 za Riyal mu kurwanya iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 yavuze ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato ibice byibasiwe n'iki cyorezo, ko abantu bonyine bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Hatangajwe gahunda zo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imigi, ariko n'ubwo bimeze bityo, urujya n'uruza rwari rukomeje mu buryo bwagutse hagati y'imigi kugeza nyuma y'umwaka mushya w'Abaperesi wa Navroz.
Mu kwezi kwa kabiri, Irani yabaye ikigo cya mbere cy'icyorezo nyuma y'Ubushinwa.
Hagati y'ibyifuzo byo guhisha icyorezo cya Iran, ibihugu birenga icumi byakurikiranye ibibazo byabo kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, byerekana ko icyorezo cyari gikomeye kurusha 388 leta ya Irani yari imaze gutangaza kugeza kuri iyo tariki.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yahagaritswe ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, nyuma y'uko abadepite 23 muri 290 bayisuzumye bagasanga banduye virusi.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura nta kirogoya abantu bafungiwe mu buryo bw'amahoro kubera guhakana ihohoterwa ry'uburenganzira bwa muntu, ndetse no kurekura by'agateganyo izindi mfungwa zifite uburenganzira.
Yavuze kandi ko ahantu abantu bafungirwa nk'ibigo by'ihamba, aho usanga nta buvuzi buhagije, hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwiza virusi.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, umubare munini cyane kuva iki cyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki n'abategetsi ba leta 12 bariho cyangwa bahoze muri Irani barapfuye.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, muri Irani, buri saha habonekaga abarwayi bashya 50 ba coronavirus, buri minota 10 hagapfa umuntu umwe.
Umukozi wa OMS avuga ko umubare w'abanduye ushobora kuba ukubye inshuro eshanu uw'abanduye muri Irani.
Hari n'abandi bavuga ko ibihano Amerika yafatiye Irani bishobora kuba byaratumye icyo gihugu kidashobora guhangana n'icyorezo.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku burenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu byoroherezwa ibihugu byinshi, harimo na Irani, byibasiwe cyane n'icyorezo cyugarije isi.
Ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo mu Butaliyani ryemejwe ku ya 31 Mutarama ubwo abagenzi babiri b'Abashinwa bapimwe SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Kubera ko umubare w'abandura wiyongereye cyane, leta y'Ubutaliyani yahagaritse ingendo zose z'indege zijya n'izisubira mu Bushinwa ndetse itangaza ko ari mu bihe by'ubukungu.
Lombardi yabonetse nyuma y'uko ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare habonetse itsinda ry'abantu batandukanye banduye COVID-19, batangiye kubarurwa mu bantu 16 bemejwe. Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya ryo kugabanya icyorezo, ryashyizeho gahunda yo gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50.000 bo mu mirenge 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe, Giuseppe Conte, yavuze ko nta muntu uzinjira cyangwa ngo asohoke mu turere twatewe n'iki cyorezo.
Amategeko yo guhagarika ibikorwa by'akazi n'imikino yamaze gutangwa muri ako karere. "Ku ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na kaminuza bifungwa burundu kubera abantu 100 bapfuye mu Butaliyani".
Imikino yose y'ingenzi, harimo imikino ya Serie A, yagombaga kubera mu kibuga gifunze kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yahagaritswe nibura ukwezi.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Kanete yategetse ko hafungwa hafi ubucuruzi bwose, uretse amasuporo n'amaduka y'imiti. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ishuri ry'Ubutaliyani ry'Ubuvuzi, Ubuvuzi, Gusubiza no Gucunga Abarwayi (SIAARTI) ryasohoye amabwiriza y'ubuvuzi agena uburyo bwo kuvurwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwatsinze Ubushinwa mu guhitana abantu 3,405 bishwe n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus ku isi.
Byari byatangajwe ko ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, Uburusiya bwohereje mu Butaliyani indege icyenda z'ingabo zitwaye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Mu Butaliyani, kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, hari abantu 128,948 bamaze kwandura, 158,87 bapfuye, 218,15 barakize, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN yagaragaje ko umubare munini w'abageze mu za bukuru bo mu Butaliyani, hamwe no kudashobora gupima abantu bose banduye virusi kugeza ubu, bishobora gutuma habaho igipimo cy'urupfu kinini.
Igisubizo cy'u Bwongereza kuri virusi cyagaragaye nk'icyoroshye kurusha ibindi bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, nta buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kwirinda cyangwa gutandukanya abaturage byari byarafatiwe abaturage bayo na guverinoma y'u Bwongereza.
Ibi byagize ingaruka ku butegetsi, aho bwarwanyijwe kubera ko butashoboye kubona umuvuduko n'uburemere bwo gusubiza ibibazo abaturage bahura nabyo. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje ko abantu bagomba kwirinda ingendo zidakenewe no kwirinda imikoranire, abantu bagakora bari mu rugo igihe bishoboka, kandi bakirinda ahantu hahurira abantu benshi, nko mu tubari, mu mazu y'uburiro n'ahantu haberamo amakinamico.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko ahantu hose ho kwidagadurira nk'inzoga n'imyidagaduro, nk'inzoga n'imyidagaduro, bigomba gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi yizeza gutanga 80% by'umushahara w'abakozi kugeza ku £ 2500 buri kwezi, kugirango birinde ubushomeri mu bihe by'amakuba. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira abantu babiri cyangwa barenze, guhagarika ingendo no gukora imirimo yo hanze gusa.
Ibyo bitandukanye n'uko byahoze, kuko iyo myigaragambyo yashoboraga gutuma abapolisi bafatirwa ibihano kandi abantu bakirukanwa.
Ibigo byinshi byategetswe gufungwa, uretse ibikorwa byafashwe nk "ibikenewe cyane" birimo amasuporo, amaduka y'ubuvuzi, amaduka acuruza ibikoresho by'ibikorwaremezo, ibiro by'ibikoresho by'ibikoresho by'ibikoresho by'ibikoresho, na garages.
Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko yanduye COVID-19 yongeye kugaragara ku itariki ya 20 y'ukwezi kwa mbere muri leta ya Pacific Northwest muri leta ya Washington, mu gihugu cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, mu gihe yari avuye i Wuhan ku itariki ya 15 y'ukwezi kwa mbere.
Ku itariki ya 29 Mutarama, hashyizweho itsinda ry'abashinzwe kurwanya icyorezo cya Coronavirus muri White House.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mu buzima rusange, kandi buhagarika ingendo zituruka mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, ikigo cy'ubutegetsi cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima rusange, Center for Disease Control, cyatangaje ko cyakoze ibikoresho by'igerageza.
Nubwo byari bimeze bityo, kubera ko Amerika yari ifite umubare muto w'abagerageza, icyo gihe ntibari bazi neza uko icyo cyorezo cyari giteye.
Ibizamini byatangiye guhungabana kubera ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi by'ububanyi n'amahanga (byakozwe n'ibigo by'uburezi, ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibitaro) bitemewe na leta ya Canada kugeza mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Gashyantare, ndetse n'ibipimo by'ibanze by'abantu byateganyijwe mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe kugira ngo bemererwe gukora ibizamini (bituma hagomba gutangwa amabwiriza ya muganga).
Kugeza ku ya 27 Mutarama, Washington Post yatangaje ko muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika hakorewe ibizamini bitarenga 4000.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, Atlantic yatangaje ko hasigaye ibipimo 14 000.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko abantu bafite ibimenyetso byinshi n'amategeko y'abaganga yo gupima bifata amasaha cyangwa iminsi kugira ngo ibipimo byemezwe. Guverineri Jay Insley yatangaje ko leta yihutirwa ubwo urupfu rwa mbere rwagaragaraga muri Amerika mu mujyi wa Washington ku ya 29 Gashyantare, igikorwa cyaje gukurikiraho vuba na bwangu n'ibindi bihugu.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yahagaritswe ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, kandi mu kwezi kwa gatatu amashuri yo mu gihugu hose yari afunze. Ku itariki ya 6 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'icyorezo zo muri kaminuza ya Imperial College y'i Londres, zahanuye Amerika ku ngaruka virusi ya corona ishobora kugira ku gihugu.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ryo kwishyura amafaranga yo kwishyura y'inyongera ya Coronavirus Preparedness and Response Act, aha inzego z'igihugu $8.3 mu nkunga yihutirwa yo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho ingamba ku rugendo rw'abakozi, akuraho inama, kandi atera inkunga abakozi gukora bavuye mu rugo.
Imikino n'ikirere byasubitswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko hari iminsi 30 yo guhagarika ingendo ziturutse mu Bwongereza n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Bukeye bwaho, bongereye ingamba zo guhuza u Bwongereza na Ireland.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko habayeho ikibazo cy'ubukungu bw'igihugu, bituma amafaranga y'igihugu agera ku byo yari akeneye kugira ngo iki kibazo gikemuke.
Mu ntangiriro z'itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ubucuruzi bwinshi muri Amerika bwafunze cyangwa bugabanya amasaha y'akazi mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, leta zose 50 n'akarere ka Columbia byari byemejwe. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, New York City yari ifite abantu 10,700 banduye coronavirus, baruta umubare w'abanduye Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko kwirinda abantu kugaragara ko hari icyo bihindura, kuko imibare y'abanduye yagabanutse kuva ku minsi 2.0 kugeza ku minsi 4.7.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, New York City yari ifite abantu 32308 banduye, naho 672 bahitanywe na virusi. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ni zo zari zifite abantu benshi banduye virusi ya corona kurusha ibindi bihugu byose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ibinyamakuru ku ya 30 Werurwe, Perezida Trump w'Amerika yongeyeho amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu ku buryo batagira aho bahurira n'abandi kugeza ku ya 30 Mata.
