Imyumvire y'ubutegetsi bwa Trump ku byerekeye ikibazo cy'ubukungu muri rusange yari yarabaye iy'ubushyamirane kandi y'ubushyamirane.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Amerika n'abatanga ibitekerezo banenze Amerika kubera ko yari ikeneye kwishingikiriza ku Bushinwa mu kuzana ibikoresho by'ingenzi, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Isesengura ry'ibimenyetso by'ingendo zo mu kirere ryakoreshejwe mu gupima ikwirakwira no kumenya aho ryakwirakwiriye, kandi ryasohotse mu kwezi kwa mbere mu kinyamakuru The Journal of Travel Medicine.
Ishyirahamwe ry'indege mpuzamahanga rya International Air Transport Association ryavuze ko mu mwaka wa 2018, abagenzi benshi bavuye i Wuhan bajya i Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byatangajwe ko ari ahantu hakunzwe cyane n'abantu bajya i Wuhan.
