Abategetsi ba Australia ku itariki ya 3 n'iya 4 z'ukwezi kwa Gashyantare, bimuriye abaturage 277 mu kigo cyo gufungirwa ku kirwa cya Christmas, cyari cyongeye guhindurwa ahantu ho kwigumira mu kato, aho abo baturage bamaze iminsi 14.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, igihe indege yari itwaye abantu bavuye muri Nouvelle-Zélande yageraga i Auckland, abagenzi (bari barimo bamwe mu baturage ba Australia n'abo muri Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cy'abasirikare ba gisirikare i Whangaporoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangaje ko zizakuraho abaturage ba Amerika bari mu bwato bw'ubwato bw'ubwato bwitwa Diamond Express.
