Ibizamini bya muganga byakozwe mbere yo kuva muri Afurika y'Epfo, kandi abaturage bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus, bari mu kato kugira ngo birinde ibyago.
Abaturage ba Afurika y'Epfo bageragejwe ko batagize ubwandu ni bo bonyine basubijwe mu gihugu cyabo.
Ibyavuye mu igerageza byasohoreye abaturage bose ba Afurika y'Epfo barimo abakozi bo mu ndege, abakozi bo muri hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari muri iyi gahunda y'ubutabazi, bari mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 bari mu kigo cya The Ranch.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukuraho igice cy'ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisitiri w'ububanyi n'amahanga w'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje imfashanyo z'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bifatanyije n'itsinda ry'abakozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika mu mujyi wa Chicago kugira ngo bohereze imfashanyo mu karere ka China kagize icyorezo, bivugwa ko iryo tsinda ryabashije kohereza udupfukamunwa 50000 tw'ibimenyetso bya N95 mu bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batanze miliyoni 100 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku rukingo n'imihati yo kuvura, harimo no kurinda abaturage bari mu kaga muri Afurika no muri Afurika y'Epfo.
Interaxion yatangaje ko nyuma y'uko Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje ibipfamatwi miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan, guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatanze ibipfamatwi ibihumbi 2000 ku itariki ya 6 Gashyantare, ku gihugu cya Philippines.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Red Crown yo muri Singapore yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'u Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwohereje mu mpano Wuhan udupfukamunwa miliyoni, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje mu mpano Wuhan toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Malayziya yatangaje impano y'intoki z'ubuvuzi miliyoni 18 mu gihugu cy'Ubushinwa, Ubudage bwohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi ibihumbi 10 harimo n'imyenda irinda indwara z'ibiza, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zohereje mu mpano toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, kandi zizeza ko zizaha izindi miliyoni 100 z'amadolari mu nkunga y'amafaranga ibihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'impuguke mu Butaliyani kugira ngo bibashe guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho by'ibizamini bya miliyoni 1.1 muri Addis Ababa muri Ethiopia, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'imyenda yo kurinda amagara ibihumbi 60 yo gukwirakwiza muri Afurika yunze ubumwe.
Nyuma yo kohereza ibikoresho by'ibizamini 5000 muri Panama, udupfukamunwa 100.000 n'ibikoresho bitanu byo guhumeka.
Ma kandi yatanze imfashanyo z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada. Ubuholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Czech byatangaje impungenge ku masike n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yakuye ibikoresho by'ibipimo bya coronavirus byakozwe n'Abashinwa bigera ku 58,000 byari bifite igipimo cy'ubwiringiro cya 30% gusa, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwasabye ko byasubizwa udupfukamunwa twacyo 600,000 twari dufite inenge twakozwe n'Abashinwa.
U Bubiligi bwasabye ko hafungurwa udupfukamunwa 10.000 tutakiri mu bubiko, twitwa ko twavuye mu Bushinwa ariko tukaba twari twemewe ko twavuye muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, inkunga y'Ubushinwa yakiriwe neza mu bihugu byo muri Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangiye ibikorwa by'ubutabazi byihutirwa mu bihugu byateye imbere.
OMS yashimye abayobozi b'u Bushinwa ku bw'imihati bashyiraho mu gucunga no gukumira icyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004 aho abategetsi b'Abashinwa bashinjwaga ubutasi, bigatuma imihati yo gukumira no kugenzura icyorezo idakomera, n'ikibazo cyo muri iki gihe aho leta y'u Burayi yatangaga amakuru buri gihe kugira ngo yirinde guhangayika mu gihe cy'umwaka mushya w'izuba.
Mu gusubiza ku cyemezo cy'abategetsi ba OMS cyo guhagarika ingendo muri Wuhan ku ya 23 Mutarama, uhagarariye OMS, Goden Gilley, yavuze ko iyi nama ya OMS itari iboneye kandi ko yagaragazaga ko biyemeje kugabanya icyorezo aho cyibasiye cyane, avuga ko ari "ikintu kitari cyabayeho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Nyuma yo kwemezwa kw'ubwandu bw'abantu buturuka ku bantu mu Bushinwa ku ya 30 Mutarama, no kwiyongera kw'imibare y'abandura mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima mpuzamahanga mu Bushinwa (EHIC), kikaba ari icya gatandatu ku isi mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya grippe mu mwaka wa 2009, nyuma yo gushyiraho ingamba zo kurwanya icyorezo cya grippe.
Tedros Adhanom, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa WHO, yavuze ko PHEYIC ari ingorabahizi y'ikwirakwira ku isi, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite umushahara muto n'uhagati aho imibereho y'ubuzima idafite ubushobozi.
Mu gusubiza ku byemezo by'ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta ngamba zitari ngombwa zigomba gufatwa zihagarika ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi" kandi ko "OMS idashishikariza ko habaho guhagarika ubucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga inkunga ya miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gufasha mu kwitegura mu bihugu bifite ubukungu buciriritse, aho yabonaga ko ari ngombwa gufasha ibihugu bitagira uburyo bwo kumenya abantu banduye, nubwo byatangiye kwandura.
Tedrosny yakomeje avuga ko "dukomeye nk'udutsiko twacu duto cyane" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "kwishora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura menshi ejo". Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru, WHO yahishuye ko icyorezo ari COVID-19.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, Antonio Guterres, yemeye ko azatanga imbaraga z'umuryango w'abibumbye wose kugira ngo uhindure ibintu.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bibazo by'ikibazo ryashyizweho, kandi ryemerewe guhuza ibisubizo by'umuryango w'abibumbye, nk'uko WHO ibivuga, bituma bashobora kwibanda ku bisubizo by'ubuzima, kandi ibindi bigo bigakoresha ubuhanga bwabo mu guhangana n'ingaruka z'imibereho, ubukungu n'iterambere birambuye.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ry'abashyize hamwe hamwe hamwe n'u Bushinwa ryashyizweho na OMS mu rwego rwo gutanga impuguke mpuzamahanga n'iz'umuryango w'abibumbye mu rwego rwo gufasha mu buyobozi bw'igihugu mu Bushinwa no gusuzuma ubukana bw'icyorezo n'ubwandu binyuze mu gukora amahugurwa no guhura n'inzego z'ingenzi ku rwego rw'igihugu, no gusura uturere n'imidugudu ku rwego rw'intara n'igihugu kugira ngo barebe ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza. Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "hari byinshi bigomba gukorwa mu guhangana n'icyorezo cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus cyugarije isi" kandi ko nubwo isi yose igomba gukomeza kwitegura icyorezo, iki gihugu kigomba gukomeza kwitegura icyorezo.
Mu gusubiza iki cyorezo cyabaye muri Irani, WHO yohereje itsinda ry'imirimo ry'ubumwe kugira ngo rigenzure uko ibintu bimeze. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba WHO bavuze ko igenzura ry'ibyago bya coronavirus ku isi rizamurwa kuva ku "cyorezo" kugeza ku "cyorezo cy'icyorezo" ku rwego rwo hejuru.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, mu itangazo yatanze, yavuze ko iki ari igihe cyo gusuzuma imimerere ya buri gihugu ku isi.
Yongeyeho ko uburyo bwiza bwo gusubiza bishobora gufasha isi kwirinda ikibi kurusha ibindi.
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu atemeza ko abayobozi b'ubuzima rusange bagomba gutangaza ko iki ari icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko gutangaza ko ari icyorezo ku isi, bivuze ko twemera ko buri muntu wese uri ku isi azahura n'iki cyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS) watangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo ku isi.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko WHO "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ubwiyongere n'ubukana by'icyorezo ndetse n'inzego z'umutekano muke z'ubushomeri". WHO yanenzwe cyane kubera ibimenyetso by'uko isi yose yataye umurongo, harimo gutangaza mu buryo butunguranye ko ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange no gushyiraho icyorezo cy'icyorezo.
Mu byatangajwe harimo inyandiko isaba ko Tedros Adhanom, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa WHO, yegura, yasinywe n'abantu 733.000 kugeza ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu zisaga icumi zasabye ko hakorwa ibishoboka byose kugira ngo uburenganzira bwa buri muntu bubahirizwe mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Abo bahanga bavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo kugira icyo akora ngo akize ubuzima bwe, kandi ko ari inshingano ya leta.
Iryo tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura ibikoresho cyangwa kubura ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima bitagomba gukoreshwa nk'isobanura yo gutandukanya itsinda runaka.
Impuguke zashimangiye ko abantu bose bafite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abakomoka mu moko mato, abatishoboye, abatagira aho baba, abakennye cyane, abafunzwe, impunzi n'abandi bantu batagira ingano bakeneye ubufasha bwa leta.
Ibigo bya Leta mpuzamahanga birimo gukemura ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza byatewe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi mu by'Ubukungu n'Iterambere (OECD) ryatangije urubuga rutanga amakuru ajyanye n'uburyo bwo gusubiza ku isi hose, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku migambi yo guha imbaraga sisitemu y'ubuzima n'ubukungu bw'isi, kugeza ku gukemura ingaruka z'imihango yo gufunga no guhagarika ingendo, ikigo cya digitale kirimo gukurikirana gahunda z'igihugu, kandi kigamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga ku bindi no koroshya igisubizo cy'isi yose ku ngorane za coronavirus.
Minisitiri w'ibiro by'abaminisitiri muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Michael Glove w'Ibiro by'abaminisitiri mu Bwongereza na Eduardo Bolsonaro w'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Bresil, Jair Bolsonaro, nabo banenze leta y'Ubushinwa kubera uburyo ikoranabuhanga ry'isi yose ryatangiriye mu ntara y'Ubushinwa ya Hubei.
Abayobozi benshi b'ishyaka ry'aba-communist ry'u Bushinwa (CPC) ku rwego rw'intara birukanywe kubera uburyo bakemuye ibikorwa byo gutandukanya abantu mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, byerekana ko batishimiye uko ishyaka ry'aba-politike ryashyizweho ryitabiriye icyo cyorezo.
Bamwe mu banenga bavuga ko iyo ngingo yari igamije gukiza Xi Jinping, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa, uburakari bw'abaturage ku cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Abashinwa, nka Zhao Lijian, bahakanye ko icyorezo cya mbere cya coronavirus cyavuye i Wuhan, bashyigikira igitekerezo cy'uko COVID-19 yatangiriye muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubuyobozi bwa Donald Trump bwo muri Amerika bwise coronavirus "virusi y'Abashinwa" cyangwa "virusi ya Wuhan", buvuga ko Ubushinwa "bwatumye virusi ikomera cyane ku buryo yageze aho ihinduka icyorezo ku isi" bamwe mu banenga bavuga ko ari ugushyira imbere ubwoko n'uko "ubutegetsi bwe bwarananiwe kugenzura icyorezo".
Ikinyamakuru The Daily Beast cyakiriye telegaramu ya leta ya Amerika yavugaga ko umugambi wo gushuka umwanzi wari watangiriye mu nama y'umutekano w'igihugu, ivuga ko uwo mugambi wari "ibintu byose ku Bushinwa".
Turabwirwa ko tugomba kugerageza gusohora ubutumwa mu buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose, haba mu biganiro by'abanyamakuru cyangwa ku mateleviziyo. Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Politiki y'amahanga na Bloomberg byatangaje ko kugerageza kohereza imfashanyo mu duce twibasiwe na virusi y'Ubushinwa ari uburyo bwo kwamamaza ku isi hose.
Umuyobozi w'umushinga w'ububanyi n'amahanga w'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, Joseph Borel, yaburiye ko "ubufatanye mu bya politiki" ari kimwe mu bintu by'ubutegetsi bw'isi, harimo no guharanira ubutegetsi.
Borrell yavuze kandi ko Ubushinwa butuma abantu bumva ko ari bwo bufatanye bufite inshingano kandi bwiringirwa kurusha Amerika.
Ubushinwa bwasabye Amerika gukuraho ibihano kuri Syria, Venezuela na Iran, ndetse buvuga ko bwatanze imfashanyo kuri Venezuela na Iran.
Imfashanyo ya Jack Ma y'ibirashe 10 000 yagombaga kujya i Cuba yahagaritswe ku itariki ya 3 Mata kubera ibihano bya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Abategetsi ba Amerika barashinjwa kandi ko bakoresheje amafaranga y'ubufasha bw'ibindi bihugu mu gukusanya amafaranga y'ubufasha.
Mu bindi bihugu, harimo n'u Budage, Ositaliya n'u Busuwisi, Repubulika ya Czech n'u Butaliyani, na ho hagiye havuka impaka ku bijyanye no kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe ibikoresho by'ubwonko bibarirwa mu magana byari byatanzwe na Espagne.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani ishinje EU kubura ubumwe mu gihugu cyibasiwe na virusi.
Maurice Masari, Ambasaderi w'u Butaliyani muri EU, yavuze ko "Ubushinwa bwonyine ari bwo bwatanze igisubizo cy'amajyaruguru".
Nta gushidikanya, ibyo si ikimenyetso cyiza cy'ubumwe bw'u Burayi".
Mu kiganiro kuri telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani Giuseppe Conte ku wa 22 Werurwe, Perezida w'Uburusiya Vladimir Putin yavuze ko ingabo z'Uburusiya ziteganya kohereza imiti, imodoka zihariye zo guhanagura indwara n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyasubiyemo amagambo yavuzwe n' "umuntu ukomeye mu bya politiki" atazwi, kivuga ko 80% by'imfashanyo zatanzwe n'u Burusiya zidakoreshwa cyangwa ngo zikoreshwe na Italia.
Uwo muyobozi yashinje u Burusiya ko bwagize gahunda yo gutesha agaciro "ibya politiki n'ububanyi n'amahanga".
Perezida wa Lombardy Attilio Fontana na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'u Butaliyani Luigi de Maio bahakanye ibivugwa n'itangazamakuru, ndetse banashimira.
Uburusiya na bwo bwo bwohereje indege itwara abafite ubumuga muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Pskov, yavuze ko "mu gutanga ubufasha ku bakorana na Amerika, [Putin] ashyira mu gaciro ko igihe abacuruzi b'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho by'ibijyanye na byo bazaba bakomeje, na bo bazatanga umusanzu mu gihe bibaye ngombwa".
Gahunda ya NATO yo guhuza ingabo za "Defender 2020" mu Budage, Polonye, n'ibihugu by'Abanya-Baltic, izaba ari gahunda nto cyane, ikaba ari imwe mu z'ingenzi cyane mu mateka ya NATO kuva intambara y'ubukonje irangira.
Kate Hudson, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango uharanira Ihagarikwa ry'Ibirwanisho bya Nikleyeri, yagize icyo avuga kuri Defender 2020 agira ati: "Muri iki gihe cy'ibibazo by'ubuzima rusange, iyi gahunda ntabwo iteza akaga ingabo za Amerika n'izindi ngabo z'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi gusa, ahubwo iteza akaga abaturage b'ibihugu bakoreramo". Leta ya Irani yahuye n'iki cyorezo kandi imaze kwandura abadepite bagera kuri babiri na 15 barimo cyangwa bahoze ari abanyapolitiki.
Perezida wa Irani, Hassan Rouhani, yandikiye abayobozi b'isi ibaruwa ku mugaragaro ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe 2020 asaba ubufasha, avuga ko igihugu cye kigorwa no guhangana n'iki cyorezo kubera ko Amerika yafashe ingamba zo kucyirinda. Iki cyorezo cyatumye Amerika ihitamo gushyiraho gahunda z'imibereho myiza zisanzwe mu bindi bihugu bikize, zirimo Universal Health Care, Universal Child Care, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango gihemba n'amafaranga menshi yo kwita ku buzima rusange.
Impuguke mu bya politiki zatangaje ko ibyo bizagira ingaruka mbi ku matora ya perezida wa 2020 ya Donald Trump.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "imihati idafite ishingiro yo gutandukanya" y'u Buyapani ubwo yatangazaga ko umuntu wese uzava muri Koreya y'Epfo azashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri mu duce dushyizweho na leta.
Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo mu mizo ya mbere wari waratatanye cyangwa wivanga mu bisubizo Perezida Moon Jae-in yatanze ku bibazo byari bihari.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon yahanwa cyangwa se bagashimira Moon ku buryo leta yafashe iki cyorezo, bityo igihugu kigashyiraho amategeko y'ubutabazi mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo cyugarije isi.
Hari bamwe mu banenga bavuga ko ibyo bishobora guha ubutegetsi uburyo bwo gukomeza ubutegetsi.
Muri Hongiriya, Inteko Ishinga Amategeko yabo yemeye ko Minisitiri w'Intebe Viktor Orban akomeza gutegeka igihe kitarondoreka, ko yatangaza ko amatora n'inteko ishinga amategeko byasubitswe, ko abatangaza amakuru atari yo ku cyorezo bakurwaho, ndetse ko leta igomba guhangana n'ikibazo.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyagaragaye ko cyatewe n'ibintu byinshi birimo ibura ry'ibikoresho by'ibikoresho, byatewe n'ikoreshwa ry'ibikoresho byo guhangana n'icyorezo ku isi, kugura mu buryo bwo guhungabana no guhagarika inganda n'ingendo.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze umuburo ku kibazo cy'ibiyobyabwenge n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, bitewe n'uko ababikeneye biyongereye ndetse n'ababikoreshaga bagahagarika.
Mu bice byinshi, abantu baguye mu kantu bagura ibintu, bituma ibicuruzwa by'ibanze birimo ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku n'amazi yafashe mu mazi, biva ku isoko bikagenda, bituma habaho ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibikoresho.
Ibigo by'ikoranabuhanga byibanze byakanguriwe gutinda gutumiza ibicuruzwa by'ikoranabuhanga.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi wa WHO Tedros Adhanam, ibipimo by'ibikoresho byo kurinda umubiri byongereye inshuro 100.
Ibi byatumye ibiciro byiyongeraho inshuro 20 z'ibiciro bisanzwe, ndetse n'ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi bitangira gutinda mu byumweru bine cyangwa bitandatu.
Ibi byatumye hakomeza kubaho ikibazo cy'ibikoresho byo kwirinda ku mubiri ku isi hose, kandi OMS yatanze umuburo ko bishobora gushyira mu kaga abakozi b'ubuzima.
Mu gihugu cya Ositaraliya, icyorezo cyatumye abacuruzi b'ibiyobyabwenge ba Daigo babona uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Ibyo byatumye hari ibigo by'ubucuruzi by'ibanze bibangamira ibura ry'ibiribwa by'abana, ndetse na leta ya Ositaraliya irabyanga. Nubwo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani n'akarere ka Wuhan hari imibare myinshi y'abanduye COVID-19 n'ibyifuzo byinshi by'ibiribwa bizaba, byombi byaracitse ku icumu ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba zo guhagarika ubucuruzi bw'ibiribwa n'ubucuruzi butemewe n'amategeko by'ibikoresho by'ibanze by'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani, zagize icyo zigeraho, bityo bituma hatabaho ibura ry'ibiribwa mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani, umusaruro w'ubuhinzi ntiwagabanutse cyane kubera ko hari byinshi byagiye biboneka, ariko abahagarariye inganda bavuga ko ibiciro bishobora kuzamuka.
Mu gihe amazu y'ubucuruzi ya Wuhan yari afite ibitabo by'ibiribwa byuzuye, byari iby'igihe gito, abategetsi b'u Bushinwa batangiye gufungura inyama z'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage bahabwe ibyokurya bihagije.
Mu Butaliyani, hari amategeko nk'ayo, asaba abahinzi kubika ibiribwa mu gihe habaye ibintu byihutirwa.
Ikigo cy'itangazamakuru cyo ku wa 16 Werurwe cyatangaje ko ubukungu bw'Ubushinwa bwagize ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 kubera ingamba zafashwe na leta y'Ubushinwa zo kwirinda ikwirakwira rya virusi, ndetse n'ubucuruzi bw'ibicuruzwa byagabanutseho 20.5%.
Mu gihe Ubushinwa ari igihugu cy'ubukungu bukomeye kandi ari na cyo gikora inganda, icyorezo cya virusi kigaragara nk'ikibazo gikomeye ku bukungu bw'isi.
Umwanditsi witwa Agathe Demarys wo mu kigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubukungu, yavuze ko amasoko azakomeza guhungabana kugeza igihe ingaruka zishoboka zizaba zigeze ku bantu.
Muri Mutarama 2020, hari abashakashatsi bavuze ko ubukungu bw'isi buzagabanuka bitewe n'iki cyorezo, ku buryo buzarenga igihe cy'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004.
