Ibizamini byo mu mavuriro by'indwara ya Coronavirus yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero 2019 (COVID-19) na SARS-CoV-2 bifitanye isano, birimo uburyo bwo kumenya ko virusi iriho no kumenya umuti wa virusi uvuka mu gisubizo cy'ubwandu.
Ikigeragezo cya virusi cyemezwa na RT-PCR, igaragaza RNA ya virusi ya corona.
Iki ni ikigeragezo cyihariye kandi cyakozwe kugirango kibashe kumenya gusa RNA ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Ikoreshwa mu kumenya niba hari ubwandu buherutse cyangwa se bwamaze kubaho.
Ibizamini bya Antibiyotike bishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima (Serology) no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini bya antibiyotike bigaragaza umubare w'abantu barwaye, harimo abantu bafite ibimenyetso bike cyane cyangwa nta bimenyetso.
Ibizamini bizatuma hagaragara umubare nyawo w'abapfa n'uko abantu bafite ubwirinzi.
Kubera ibipimo bike, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku ikwirakwira rya virusi mu baturage bacyo kugeza muri Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyakoze ibizamini birenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini ku bipimo byakozwe hagati y'ibihugu.
Ibi bishobora no kugira ingaruka ku mibare y'abapfa, ariko mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe bishobora kuba ari ibintu bidashyize mu gaciro.
Ibipimo by'ubuhumekero bifatirwa mu buryo butandukanye, harimo mu gihe cy'imikorere y'ibisate by'amaboko cyangwa mu gihe cy'imikorere y'amaboko, bishobora gukorwa hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo kuvugurura imikorere y'imikorere y'ibisate by'amaboko (RRT-PCR).
Ibisubizo bikunze kuboneka mu masaha make cyangwa se mu minsi ibiri.
Iperereza rya RT-PCR ry'ubuhumekero mu muhogo ryerekana neza icyumweru cya mbere cy'uburwayi.
Nyuma y'aho, virusi ishobora kuva mu muhogo, kandi ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha mu buryo bwihuse.
Mu cyumweru cya kabiri cyo gupima abantu banduye, ubundi bashobora gukoreshwa mu gupima umwuka mu buryo bw'ubuhumekero (suction catheter) cyangwa bakoresha imyanda yo mu gihe cyo guhekenya (pseudotermie).
Imwe mu miti ya mbere ya PCR yakoreshejwe mu buryo bw'igihe nyacyo (RRT-PCR) mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga, yatangijwe muri Charity i Berlin muri Mutarama 2020, ikaba ari yo yari ishingiro ry'imiti 250,000 yatanzwe n'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) kugira ngo itangwe.
