Iki kizamini kigaragaza ko hari ubwoko bwa "E" bugizwe na virusi ya corona yose ya beta, ndetse n'ubundi bwoko bwa RdRp bwihariye kuri SARS-CoV-2. BGI Group ni imwe mu zindi nganda za mbere zabonye uruhushya rw'ubutabazi rw'ikigo cy'igihugu cy'ubuvuzi cy'Ubushinwa (National Medical Products Administration) ku bikoresho bya SARS-CoV-2 bishingiye kuri PCR mu Bushinwa.
