Muri Werurwe 2020, American College of Radiology yasabye ko "CT idakoreshwa nk'igerageza rya mbere rikoreshwa mu gupima cyangwa gusuzuma COVID-19". CDC yasabye ko PCR ikoreshwa mu gupima mbere ya byose muri Werurwe 2020.
Igikoresho cya IgG na IgM, ni byo bikora umuti wa virusi, mu gihe umubiri uba utangiye guhangana n'ubwandu.
