Ibipimo byinshi byagenewe mu bigo by'ubushakashatsi bishobora gukorwa mu buryo bwa 'automated systems' (SAS) mu gihe runaka, ariko bigakorwa bitewe n'ibiciro by'ibikoresho bya buri sisitemu.
Nubwo hari ingero nyinshi zishobora gukoreshwa mu gukurikirana ibisubizo by'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, ingero imwe y'amaraso yo mu gice cy'ubuhumekero ni yo ikoreshwa mu gihe cy'ibicurane by'amaraso.
Poroteyine yo mu maraso (POCT) ikoreshwa mu kuvura uruhu, mu kuvura uruhu hakoreshejwe amaraso.
Bitandukanye n'uburyo bwa PCR, nta gushakishwa kwa mbere kw'ibipimo bikenewe. Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatangaje amazina y'ibikoresho 29 byatanze inama ku kigo nk'uko bikenewe bityo bikaba bishoboka ko bitanga ibipimo byabyo bya antibiyotike.
Kugeza ku ya 7 Mata 2020, FDA yemeje igerageza rimwe gusa mu gihe ryemewe mu buryo bw'ibanze. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, EuroEmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics na Epitome Diagnostics byahawe uburenganzira n'umuryango w'ibihugu by'i Burayi ku bikoresho by'igerageza ryabo, bishobora gupima IgG na IgA mu maraso mu gihe virusi yanduye.
Ubushobozi bw'iki kizamini ni bwinshi ku buryo hari amasampula abarirwa mu magana ashobora gusuzumwa mu masaha make, bityo bikaba byihuta cyane kurusha ibizamini bya PCR bisanzwe bifasha mu gupima virusi ya RNA.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Mata, Ubwongereza bwabonye ko nta na kimwe mu bikoresho by'ibizamini bya antibiyotike bwaguze cyari gikwiye gukoreshwa.
Hong Kong ifite gahunda yo kuba abarwayi bakekwaho kuba barwaye bashobora kuguma mu rugo, "Urwego rw'Ubutabazi ruzaha umurwayi icyuma cy'ibipimo", bakayivamo, bakayisubiza, hanyuma nyuma y'igihe runaka bakagira ibisubizo by'ibizamini. NHS y'u Bwongereza yatangaje ko irimo gukora ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze ku buryo abarwayi bakekwaho kuba barwaye bakorerwa ibizamini mu rugo, aho batazongera guteza abandi indwara iyo baje mu bitaro cyangwa ngo hakoreshwe ambulansi kugira ngo bakoreshwe mu guhanagura indwara.
Ibigo by'ubushakashatsi by'ibanze byafashije Koreya y'Epfo gukora ibizamini byihuse, byuzuye kurusha ibindi bihugu byose. Mu Budage, ku itariki ya 2 Werurwe, Ishyirahamwe ry'Abavuzi ba Bihebuje ry'Ubwisungane mu Buzima ryemeje ko rifite ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini bigera ku 12,000 ku munsi mu buryo bw'ubushakashatsi, mu gihe mu cyumweru gishize ryakoraga 10.700.
Iyo muganga abisabye, amafaranga y'ubwishingizi yishyurwa.
Nk'uko byemezwa na perezida w'ikigo Robert Koch, Ubudage bufite ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu 160,000 buri cyumweru.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, ibizamini byo gutwara abantu mu modoka byari byatangiwe mu mijyi myinshi.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe 2020, umubare w'abamaze gupimwa mu Budage ntiwari uzwi, kuko hakozwe abarwayi gusa.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere mu kigo cy'ubushakashatsi bwerekanye ko nibura 4,83,295 by'ibipimo byasuzumwe kugeza mu cyumweru cya 12/2020 cy'ikirangaminsi ndetse no mu cyumweru cya 12/2020, maze 33,491 by'ibipimo (6.9%) byerekana ko byanduye SARS-CoV-2. Abashakashatsi mu bitaro bya Technion na Rambam muri Isiraheli bakoze uburyo bwo gusuzuma ibipimo by'abarwayi 64 icyarimwe, aho ibipimo byose byahurijwe hamwe, hanyuma hakorwa ubundi bushakashatsi gusa mu gihe ibipimo byose byabonetse. Ku ya 5 Gashyantare 2020, ibigo by'ubushakashatsi bya Wuhan byitiriwe "Huo-han" (Icyongereza: "Gahunda") byatangije ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cya 2000 sqm, gishobora gutunganya ibipimo birenga 10,000 ku munsi.
Byubatswe mu minsi 5 ku buyobozi bwa Wang Jian washinze BGI, kandi ibi byerekana ko iyo ubushobozi bwo gupima butatangira ku gihe, Hubei yari kubona abantu 47% barenzeho kandi ikiguzi gifatika cyo gucunga abarwayi cyari kuba cyikubye kabiri.
Ibigo by'ubushakashatsi bya Huang-Yan biri mu migi 12 y'Ubushinwa, ni ukuvuga Shenzhen, Tianjin, Beijing na Shanghai, byakurikiranye ibi bikoresho by'ubushakashatsi bya Wuhan.
Kugeza ku ya 4 Werurwe 2020, ingano y'ibipimo bya buri munsi yari 50,000. Imyandikire y'ibanze, ya Origami Esage, ishobora gupima ibipimo 1122 by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 hakoreshejwe ibipimo 93 gusa.
Kugeza muri Werurwe, ibura ry'imiti n'ibura ryayo byatangiye kuba inzitizi mu igerageza ry'ubwoko bwinshi mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi, mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika.
Ibi byatumye bamwe mu banditsi batangira kugerageza uburyo bwo gutegura ibipimo, harimo gushyushya ibipimo 98 ° C (208 ° F) iminota 5 kugirango genome ya RNA ifungurwe kugirango hakorwe ibindi bizamini. Ku ya 31 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko UAE ubu ikora ibizamini bya coronavirus kubantu benshi mu baturage bayo kurusha ikindi gihugu icyo ari cyo cyose, kandi ko igiye kuzamura urwego rwo gupima kugirango igere ku baturage benshi.
Ibi byatewe n'ubushobozi bwo gutwara abantu n'ubucuruzi bw'ibiro by'ubushakashatsi mu rwego rw'abaturage by'itsinda rya 42 na BGI (byashingiye ku bigo byabo by'ubushakashatsi by'ubutabazi bya "Huo-Yan" mu Bushinwa).
Iyi laboratwari yubatswe mu minsi 14, ifite ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini bya RT-PCR ibihumbi n'ibihumbi ku munsi, kandi ni yo ya mbere ku isi ifite ubushobozi bwinshi butari mu Bushinwa.
Mu Bushinwa, mu Bufaransa, mu Budage, muri Hong Kong, mu Buyapani no muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, hatangijwe ibikorwa bitandukanye by'igerageza byibanda ku bice bitandukanye by'imiterere ya virusi ya corona.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryemeye ko u Budage bwohereza ibikoresho by'imiti mu bihugu bifite ubukungu buciriritse bitagira ubushobozi bwo kubyikorera.
Igikorwa cy'u Budage cyasohotse ku ya 17 Mutarama 2020; poroteyine yateguwe n'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara ntiyari ikiriho kugeza ku ya 28 Mutarama, bituma ibipimo biboneka muri Amerika bitinda. Mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo, Ubushinwa na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika byari bifite ibibazo ku bijyanye n'ubuziranenge bw'ibikoresho by'ipimisha, kandi ibyo bihugu na Ositaraliya ntibyashoboraga gutanga ibikoresho bihagije kugira ngo bikurikize ibyifuzo by'abahanga mu by'ubuzima.
Ahubwo, kuba ibipimo byinshi by'ubushakashatsi byarabonetse muri Koreya y'Epfo, byafashije mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Ikigo cy'igihugu cy'ubushakashatsi cya Korea y'Epfo cyakoze ubushakashatsi bwinshi mu bigo byigenga mu gihe cy'imyaka myinshi.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryasabye ko gahunda y'igerageza yongerwa, nk'uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Muri Werurwe 2020, Ubushinwa bwatanze raporo y'ibibazo by'ubwiringiro mu byuma by'igerageza.
Mu gihugu cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, CDC yateguye ibikoresho byo gupima "ibyangiritse"; nyuma yaho, leta yakuyeho inzitizi z'ubutegetsi zabuzaga abantu gukora ibizamini byigenga.
Ikigo cyasobanuye ko ibisubizo bitari byo bishobora kuba byatewe no kudakora neza mu gutoranya ibipimo cyangwa gukoresha neza ibipimo.
Minisiteri ya Espagne yavuze ko izasubiza ibikoresho byatanze ibisubizo bitari byo, ikabiha ibindi bikoresho by'ibizamini bitangwa na Shenzhen Bioeasy. Repubulika ya Czech yatanze 80% by'ibikoresho by'ibizamini by'ibizamini byatanzwe n'u Bushinwa. Slovakia yaguze ibikoresho by'ibizamini 1.2 mu Bushinwa byaje kugaragara ko bifite inenge.
Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubuzima wa Turukiya Ates Kara yavuze ko ibikoresho by'igerageza by'u Bushinwa by'u Turukiya "byari bifite amakosa menshi" kandi ko "bitakoreshejwe". Ubwongereza bwaguze ibikoresho by'igerageza by'u Bushinwa bigera kuri miliyoni 35 ariko mu ntangiriro za Mata 2020 bwatangaje ko bitakiri ngombwa.
Gupima, gukemura ibibazo by'abanduye SARS-CoV-2 no gukurikirana abanduye abandi bagaragaye ko banduye, byagize ingaruka nziza.
Abashakashatsi bo mu mujyi wa Vô, mu Butaliyani aho icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyibasiye abantu benshi, bakoze ibisubizo bibiri by'ibizamini ku baturage bagera ku 3400 mu gihe cy'iminsi igera ku icumi.
Kimwe cya kabiri cy'abanduye nta bimenyetso bagaragazaga, maze abafashwe bashyirwa mu kato.
Mu gihe abantu bari bafite ingendo nke, indwara nshya zirinzwe burundu.
Kubera ko mu 2020 icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyakwirakwiriye muri Singapore ku muvuduko muto ugereranyije n'ibindi bihugu byateye imbere, kandi nta birindiro by'urudaca byashyizweho nko gufunga amazu y'uburiro n'amazu y'ubucuruzi.
Ibirori byinshi byarahagaritswe, kandi kuva ku ya 28 Werurwe, Singapore yatangiye kubwira abaturage kuguma mu rugo, ariko amashuri yongeye gufungura ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, igihe cyagenwe nyuma y'ikiruhuko.
Ibihugu byinshi, nka Iceland na Koreya y'Epfo, byakemuye iki cyorezo binyuze mu gukurikirana ku buryo bugaragara, guhagarika ingendo zo mu gihugu, gupima no kwigunga, ariko byongeye kandi binyuze mu gufunga mu buryo budafite ubukana.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe bwagaragaje ko ibihugu byagize ibipimo byinshi by'abapfa, bifite igipimo gito cy'abapfa, bitewe n'uko bishobora kuba byarabonye abantu bafite ibimenyetso bike cyangwa nta bimenyetso.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye ko ibihugu bidafite ubushobozi bwo gupima, ndetse n'ibigo by'ubushakashatsi by'igihugu bifite ubumenyi buke kuri COVID-19, byoherezwa mu bihugu bifite ibipimo bya mbere bitanu by'abanduye COVID-19 n'ibya mbere 10 by'abanduye COVID-19 kugira ngo bifashishwe mu gupima.
Muri ibi bigo 16, 7 biri muri Aziya, 5 biri mu Burayi, 2 muri Afurika, 1 muri Amerika ya Ruguru na 1 muri Ositaraliya.
Impamvu "% y'abandura" mu mbonerahamwe iri hasi, ifitanye isano n'amabwiriza agenga ibizamini.
Mu bindi bintu byose, haba mu kugaragaza ibimenyetso cyangwa mu kutabigaragariza, ibipimo by'abandura bizaba byinshi ugereranyije n'ibihugu byageragereza abaturage bose, aho ibihugu byageragereza gusa abantu bari mu bitaro.
Gukaraba intoki (cyangwa gukaraba intoki), nanone byitwa isuku y'intoki, ni igikorwa cyo gukaraba intoki umuntu akora agamije gukuraho ubutaka, amavuta, mikorobe cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
Gukaraba intoki mu gihe runaka cy'umunsi, mu gihe cy'amasaha make cyane, bishobora gutuma indwara nyinshi zidakwirakwira, urugero nk'ibicurane n'ibicurane, kuko byibasira intoki mu kanwa.
Abantu bashobora kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero, urugero nk'ibicurane cyangwa imbeho, urugero, iyo batigeze bakaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, ku zuru cyangwa ku munwa (ni ukuvuga, ku ruhu rw'umwanda).
Igihe cy'ingenzi cyo gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni: mbere na nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero, nyuma yo gukaraba umwana cyangwa kumuhindura isutiye, mbere yo kumusuhuza, mbere yo kurya no guteka, cyangwa mbere na nyuma yo gukora ku nyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Mu gihe nta mazi n'isabune biboneka, umuntu ashobora gukaraba intoki akoresheje umufuka, ariko Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryasabye ko umuntu yakaraba intoki mu bihe bikurikira:
Mbere yo guteka, mu gihe cyo guteka na nyuma yo guteka.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindura ikinyita cyangwa gukaraba umwana wagiye mu misa.
Nyuma yo gukorora, gukorora cyangwa gukorora.
Nyuma yo gukora ku nyamaswa, ku byokurya by'inyamaswa cyangwa ku byatsi by'inyamaswa.
Isuku y'amaboko mu buvuzi ni uburyo bwo kwirinda indwara ziterwa n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa mbere yo kujya kwa muganga bishobora gutuma indwara zidakwirakwira cyangwa zikagabanuka.
Intego y'ingenzi yo gukaraba intoki mu buvuzi ni ukuzikuraho ibintu byangiza (bakteriya, virusi cyangwa ibindi binyabuzima bishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho byangiza cyangwa bishobora gutera indwara.
Ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakoresha ibiribwa cyangwa mu by'ubuvuzi, ariko ni ingenzi no ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kenshi ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'ibicurane, virusi ya corona n'izindi; gukumira indwara z'ibicurane ziterwa n'ububyimba; kugabanya indwara z'ubuhumekero;
Kandi mu kubyara mu rugo harimo no kugabanya umubare w'abana bapfa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki butunganijwe neza bushobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu barushaho kuba bakomeye.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero n'isukari ushobora kugabanuka uhereye ku guhindura ibintu byoroheje mu myitwarire, urugero nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Iyo umuntu akoze ikintu kimwe gusa, ashobora kugabanya umubare w'abahitanwa n'iyo ndwara ku kigero cya 50%.
Gushyiraho ingamba zo gukaraba intoki bishobora kugabanya igifu ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, bikaba byagereranywa no kugeza amazi meza mu baturage bafite amikoro make.
48% by'abahitanwa n'ibicurane bishobora kuba byaturutse ku gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage ku isi hose, ni bwo buryo bw'ibanze kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda ibicurane n'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye (ARIs).
Pneumonia, ari na yo ifite ARI nyinshi, ni yo mpamvu y'ibanze ituma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu bapfa, ikaba ihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 18 buri mwaka.
Imyimba n'umusonga bihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 35 buri mwaka.
UNICEF ivuga ko kubaho mu buryo bwemewe bwo gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya na nyuma yo kujya ku cyumba cy'imyambaro bishobora gukiza ubuzima bw'abantu benshi kurusha ubundi buryo bwose bwo gukingira cyangwa bwo kuvura, bigatuma umubare w'abapfa bazize isesemi ugabanukaho kimwe cya kabiri, n'uw'abapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye ugabanukaho kimwe cya kane.
Akenshi gukaraba intoki bijyanirana n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku nk'igice cy'ibikorwa by'amazi, isuku n'isuku (wash).
Gukaraba intoki birinda indwara zitera impetigo, zituruka ku kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina.
Ingaruka nke zo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora gutuma uruhu ruguma rwumye, rugakomereka.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Danimarike mu mwaka wa 2012, bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutera indwara z'uruhu, urugero nko gukorora intoki, kuruka, cyangwa indwara z'uruhu zitwa ko ari indwara z'uruhu, cyane cyane mu bakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane ni kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara yo guhangayika mu bitekerezo (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune kugira ngo ntandure ikwirakwira ry'indwara: nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero (gukaraba, gutesha, guhanagura), nyuma yo gukaraba uruhinja (guhindura isutiye), mbere yo kugaburira uruhinja, mbere yo kurya no guteka, cyangwa mbere yo gukora ku nyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko zitagifuwe.
Mu bindi bihe, uburyo bukwiye bwo gukaraba intoki kugira ngo umuntu yirinde gukwirakwiza indwara, harimo mbere na nyuma yo kuvura ibikomere cyangwa ibindi bikomere; nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa gukaraba; nyuma yo gukora ku byatsi by'inyamaswa cyangwa nyuma yo gukora ku matungo no ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, abantu ntibakoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2015 mu bihugu 54 bwerekanye ko ku kigereranyo, 38.7% by'ingo zikoresha isabune. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2014 bwagaragaje ko Arabia Saudite ari yo ifite igipimo cyo hejuru cyo gukaraba intoki ku kigero cya 95%, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ni 77%, naho mu Bushinwa ni ho hari hasi cyane ku kigero cya 23%.
Gahunda y'ubuzima bw'ibanze ishyirwa mu bikorwa n'ishami ry'uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rw'ingamba zo kubungabunga ubuzima bw'abana no kubateza imbere mu burezi.
Gucishaho udukoko kabiri mu mwaka, gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabune, no kumesa amenyo n'ibikoresho bya fluoride, ni bimwe mu bigize gahunda y'igihugu.
Ibi byakozwe neza muri Indoneziya.
Gukata udukoko duto cyane ku ruhu byongerwaho n'amazi n'isabune cyangwa imyanda.
Igikorwa cy'ibanze cy'isabune n'umutobe ni ukugabanya igihagararo cy'umuti no kongera uburyo bwo kuwusenya.
Amazi yonyine ntashobora gusukura uruhu kuko ibinure na poroteyine biboneka mu butaka bw'ibinyabuzima bitanyura mu mazi.
Ariko kandi, isuku ikorwa binyuze mu gutemba k'amazi ku buryo bukwiriye.
Kubera imiterere y'ibikoresho byacu byongera gukoreshwa, hari uburyo bwo kubona ko isabune irimo mikorobe zaturutse mu bikoresho by'ibanze twakoresheje mbere.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko udukoko dutera indwara twandura mu isabune, bwagaragaje ko udukoko dutera indwara tudashobora guturuka mu mazi, kubera ko dusenyuka bitewe n'imyuka.
CDC iracyavuga ngo "Isabune y'amazi idashobora gukoreshwa n'intoki ni nziza".
Amashanyarazi y'ibikoresho by'uburozi bya antibiotique yashyizwe ahagaragara cyane mu bantu bazi neza ubuzima.
Kugeza ubu, nta bimenyetso bifatika byerekana ko umuti wa antibiotique cyangwa umuti wica udukoko ukoreshwa mu kurwanya indwara ziterwa n'imiti.
Ariko kandi, isabune ya antibiotiki irimo imiti isanzwe ya antibiotiki, urugero nka trichlosan, ifite urutonde rurerure rw'ibinyabuzima byirinda indwara.
Ni yo mpamvu, nubwo nta miti yica udukoko yafashwe mu gihe cy'ibinyobwa byo kwica udukoko, ishobora kuba idakora nk'uko byavuzwe.
Uretse kuba ari ibiribwa bifasha mu gusukura no kurinda uruhu, hari n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuhanga nk'ibikomoka kuri pH, urugero nka aside (acide acétique, ascorbic acid, lactic acid), aside ya benzoic ikora mu kurwanya indwara, n'ibindi bikoresho bifasha mu guhumura uruhu (ibinure, vitamine, menthol, ibikomoka ku bimera). Ubushakashatsi bwimbitse bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Oregon School of Public Health bwagaragaje ko isabune ari nziza mu kwirinda indwara no gukuraho udukoko mu kanwa nk'uko bimeze ku sabuni zisanzwe zikorerwamo imiti ya triclosan.
Amazi ashyushye, meza yo gukaraba intoki, ntahagije mu kwica udukoko.
Iyo umubiri ufite ubushyuhe bwinshi, utwo ducurama twongera umuriro cyane.
Ariko kandi, amazi ashyushye ni ingirakamaro cyane kurusha amazi akonje arimo isabune mu gukuraho amavuta y'ibanze arimo ubutaka n'udukoko.
Icyakora, binyuranyije n'ibyo abantu benshi batekereza, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu rwego rwa siyansi bwagaragaje ko amazi meza adashobora kugabanya imitwaro y'ibinyabuzima byandura ku ntoki.
Umushongi w'amaboko cyangwa umuti wica udukoko ni umuti wo gusukura intoki udafite amazi.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki bitagira amazi (byitwa kandi intoki zikorana n'inzoga, intoki z'intoki z'intoki cyangwa intoki z'intoki) byatangiye gukundwa.
Byinshi muri byo biboneka mu buryo bwa gels hamwe n'ibikoresho byongerera uburemere nka karbomeri (polymeri ya acrylic acid) hamwe na isopropyl alcohol cyangwa ethanol ifatanyije, cyangwa mu buryo bw'umunyunyu wumye nka glycerine, cyangwa mu buryo bw'amavuta yoroshye gukoresha no mu buryo bw'amavuta yo kugabanya ingaruka zo gukama kwa alcohol.
Umwuka utuma umuntu agira intungamubiri nyinshi, kandi utuma umubiri ugira intungamubiri nyinshi.
Inzoga zikoreshwa mu gusukura imyanda, indwara ziterwa n'imiti nyinshi (MRSA na VRE), igituntu n'izindi mikorobe zimwe na zimwe (harimo virusi itera SIDA, herpes, RSV, virusi z'impara, Vaccinia, influenza na Hepatite) n'imyanda
Inzoga z'ibirahuri zirimo 70% bya alkali, kandi mu masegonda 30 nyuma yo kuzishyiraho, zica 99,97% (kugabanya 3.5% bingana no kugabanya 35 decibels) na 99,99% kugeza kuri 99,99% (kugabanya 4 kugeza kuri 5) ku mikorobe nyuma y'umunota umwe. Inzoga z'amaboko zirakora cyane ku mikorobe imwe, ariko ntizikora cyane ku mikorobe imwe.
Igisukari cy'amaboko gishingiye kuri alcohol ntikigira ingaruka na gato ku mikorobe nka norovirus (cyangwa Norvoc), ari yo mpamvu ikunze gutera indwara y'ubuhumekero.
Fata intoki zombi, imbere n'inyuma, hagati y'intoki zose, maze ubyandike mu mazi, mu busa cyangwa mu gishanga cya gel, mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, cyasabye ko umuntu yakwihana akoresheje umuti wa sanitiseri iyo amaze gukaraba intoki, iyo ari zo zose zigaragaza umwanda.
Kuba ari ibintu byoroshye gukoresha kandi bica udukoko duto mu buryo bwihuse, bituma abantu benshi barushaho kubikoresha, ariko ntibikwiye gusimbura gukaraba intoki neza mu gihe nta mazi n'isabune biboneka.
Gukoresha cyane sanitizer ishingiye kuri alcohol bishobora gutuma uruhu ruguha, bityo rero, ugomba kuyishyiramo imiti yo koroshya uruhu n'/cyangwa moisturizer.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, uburyohe bwo gukama bw'inzoga bushobora kugabanuka cyangwa bukarangira hakoreshejwe glycyrine cyangwa ibindi bintu bigabanya uruhu.
