Mu mwaka wa 2008, ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cy'i Londres muri kaminuza ya Westminster, cyakoze ubushakashatsi bushingiye ku byerekeranye n'isuku itanga imyenda y'ibishyimbo, imashini zimesa intoki zikoresha umwuka ushyushye n'imashini zimesa intoki z'indege zigezweho, kandi bwashyigikiwe n'ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cy'ibiro by'ishami ry'imikorere y'impu z'ibikomoka ku bice by'umubiri byo mu Burayi.
