Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro muri Afurika, nubwo hari uburyo bworoshye bwo gukaraba intoki, nta bikoresho by'ubwogero biboneka hafi y'ubwogero bwa bwite cyangwa bwa rusange.
