Guteza imbere no guhemba gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro ifatwa, kubyutsa ubumenyi ku nyungu zo gukaraba intoki no guhindura imyitwarire y'abaturage mu gihe kirekire.
