Icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cyabaye mu mwaka wa 2009 na COVID-19 mu mwaka wa 2020, byatumye ibihugu byinshi byumva akamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu kwirinda indwara zandura.
