Ikindi kandi, abantu bemerewe gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gutekereza batyo, ntibashobora gukora indi mirimo yo "guhanagura" nk'ibikorwa by'ubwitange.
Amadini asaba gukaraba intoki haba mu rwego rw'isuku no mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo. Gukoresha amazi yo gukaraba intoki, ariko kudakoresha isabune ni ukunywa intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, ni kimwe mu birori byo gukaraba intoki, birimo ababahete, abahindu, abayahudi ba Tewilah na Netilah, Abakristo ba Lavabo na ba Wudu muri Islam. Amadini asaba gukaraba intoki nyuma y'ibikorwa runaka by'isuku.
