Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi biterwa na COVID-19
Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi biterwa na COVID-19 ni uburyo bwo gukoresha ubuziranenge n'ubuzima mu kazi mu kurwanya icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Gucunga neza ibyago mu kazi biterwa n'aho umuntu akorera ndetse n'imiterere y'akazi, aho umuntu yakomotse, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage ndetse n'ibyago buri mukozi ashobora kuba afite kuri COVID-19.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ubuyobozi bw'ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi muri Amerika (OSHA), akazi gafite ibyago bike byo kwandura ni akazi gafite aho gaherera ku bantu n'abandi bakozi, aho ingamba zo kwirinda kwandura zisabwa harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kwirinda guhumeka no gusukura no gusuzuma indwara mu gihe cy'akazi.
Ibikorwa bifite ibyago byo kwandura birimo ibikorwa bisaba ko umuntu aba hafi cyangwa agirana imishyikirano ya hafi n'abandi bantu bataramenyekana cyangwa bakekwaho kwandura COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba baranduye kubera ubwandu bw'umuryango bukomeje cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Muri abo harimo abakozi bakorana n'abaturage, nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo ituwe cyane, ndetse no mu maduka manini.
Uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, ingamba zo kugenzura ibyago kuri uyu muryango zirimo kubungabunga umwuka ukoresheje imyuka ifasha guhumeka cyane, gukoresha abarinzi b'imyenda no kuba umuntu afite ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite mu gihe ahanganye na COVID-19.
OSHO yita ku bakozi b'ubuzima n'abakora mu nzu y'ibyangombwa by'indembe bagiranye isano n'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho kwandura COVID-19 nk'abari mu byiciro by'ubwandu, aho uwo mukozi yaba akora ibikorwa byo gukora aerosol cyangwa akura cyangwa agakora ibipimo by'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho kwandura COVID-19, bityo bikongera ibyago byo kwandura cyane.
Mu byiciro by'ibyago by'abakozi, harimo ibyiciro by'ubwubatsi, nk'ibyumba by'ubushyuhe bufite umwuka mubi n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite bikwiye ku kazi runaka.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kudakora bitewe n'uburwayi, kuba bagomba kwita ku bandi cyangwa gutinya ko bashobora kwandura.
Uburyo bw'ubucuruzi bushobora guhinduka, haba mu bijyanye n'ibyo umuntu akeneye n'uburyo bwo kubikenera (nk'ubucuruzi bwo kugura mu gihe cy'umuriro cyangwa kugura binyuze mu gutanga cyangwa kugura hakoreshejwe serivisi zo kugurisha).
Amaherezo, ibicuruzwa bishobora guhungabana mu turere twibasiwe cyane na COVID-19. Gahunda yo kwitegura indwara zandura no gusubiza ishobora gukoreshwa mu bikorwa byo kwirinda.
Gahunda igaragaza ibyiciro by'ibyago bifitanye isano n'aho bakorera ndetse n'akazi, birimo inkomoko y'ubwandu, ibyago bituruka mu ngo no mu mibereho y'abaturage, n'ibyago buri mukozi ashobora guhura na byo, nk'imyaka y'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Bagena uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyago by'uko byagenda, n'uburyo bwo guhagarika ibyago bishobora guterwa n'uko byagenda.
Gutegura no gusubiza indwara zandura bishobora gushingira ku bitekerezo byatanzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa urw'igihugu.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'abakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura indwara zinyuranye n'ubuzima, gukomeza imikorere y'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ziterwa n'ibindi bintu mu muyoboro w'ibikoresho byabo.
Aho ubucuruzi buba buri, bigira ingaruka ku bisubizo by'uburwayi mu baturage.
Hariho uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyago bukoreshwa cyane mu buvuzi n'umutekano mu rwego rwo gushyiraho ingamba zo kugenzura ibyago.
Mu gihe COVID-19 idashobora gukurwaho burundu, uburyo bwo kugenzura neza ni ubwubatsi, hanyuma ikoreshwa n'ubuyobozi, hanyuma ikoreshwa n'ibikoresho bya bwite.
Igenzura ryubwubatsi ririmo kurinda abakozi ibyago bijyanye n'akazi, bitagendeye ku myitwarire y'abakozi, kandi birashobora kuba igisubizo gihenze cyo gushyira mu bikorwa.
Ubuyobozi ni uguhindura politiki cyangwa imikorere y'akazi, bisaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite (PPE) bifatwa nk'ibidashobora gukoreshwa cyane kurusha ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi n'ibyangombwa, ariko bishobora gufasha mu gukumira indwara zimwe na zimwe.
PPE zose zigomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku ngaruka zikorerwa umukozi, zikagomba kuba zifite ubushobozi bwo guhagarara neza (urugero: respirateurs) kandi zikambikwa neza, zigomba kugenzurwa buri gihe, kugenzurwa no guhindurwa nk'uko bikenewe, kandi zigomba kuvanwa neza, gusukurwa neza no kubikwa neza cyangwa gutwarwa neza mu rwego rwo kwirinda kwandura.
Dukurikije Itegeko ry'Ubutegetsi bw'Ubuzima n'Umutekano mu Mirimo (OSHO), imirimo ifite ibyago bike byo kwandura ifitanye isano nkeya n'akazi hamwe n'abaturage ndetse n'abandi bakozi.
Gahunda z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zirasabwa ku buryo bwose bw'ahantu ho gukoreramo, harimo gukaraba intoki hejuru no hasi, gukangurira abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kubahiriza amabwiriza yo guhumeka harimo no gutwikira mu gihe cyo gukorora no kwitsamura, gutanga amasahani yo gushyiraho imyanda y'impu n'impapuro, gutegura itumanaho cyangwa gukora amasaha y'akazi igihe bibaye ngombwa, kwirinda abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi no gusukura no guhanagura ahantu ho gukoreramo.
Guhita umenya kandi ukagenzura abantu bashobora kwandura ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi mu kazi.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga inama ko abakozi bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bagomba kuguma mu rugo igihe cyose bamaze nibura amasaha 24 badafite umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro n'ibindi bimenyetso, kandi badafite imiti igabanya umuriro cyangwa ihindura ibimenyetso, kandi bafite politiki yo kuruhuka mu gihe cy'indwara, yemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo bitabe ku muntu urwaye wo mu muryango wabo, kandi abakozi bazi neza izo politiki.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, akazi gafite ibyago byo kwandura ku buryo buciriritse gashobora kuba gasaba ko umuntu yakora contact ya hafi ya metero esheshatu (1.8m) n'abantu bataramenyekana cyangwa bakekwaho kwandura COVID-19, ariko bitewe n'uko hashobora kuba hari ikwirakwira ry'abantu mu gace k'ubucuruzi cyangwa se umuntu ashobora kuba yaravuye mu ngendo mpuzamahanga mu gace COVID-19 yakwirakwijwe cyane.
Muri ibi harimo abakozi bafite aho bahurira n'abaturage basanzwe, nko ku mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo abantu benshi ndetse na bimwe mu bigo binini by'ubucuruzi, hamwe n'ibindi bikorwa by'ubwubatsi by'abakozi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, harimo kwinjiza mu byuma by'ubwubatsi ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi bifite ubushobozi bwo guhumeka umwuka, kongera umubare w'abantu bakoresha umwuka mu gihe batembera ahantu hakoreshwa ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi, gushyiraho inzitizi z'ibanze nk'ibikoresho bya plastiki cyangwa ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi, no gushyiraho ahantu ho gukinga no gufungira amadirishya mu rwego rw'ubutabazi.
Abakozi bafite ibyago byinshi ntibakunze gukoresha imashini zifasha guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, ingamba zikwiye zo kurinda abakozi n'abandi bantu barimo kumurinda abantu, kumushyira mu ntera y'ibirenge 6, gushyiraho umukozi w'abagenzi wo kumufasha, no kumuha agapfukamunwa cyangwa kumusaba gupfuka umunwa n'amaso ye n'impapuro z'uruhu mu gihe arimo gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Iyo umukozi w'indege afite umuriro, guhekenya cyangwa guhumeka, cyangwa iyo afashe imyanda y'umubiri cyangwa ahantu hashobora kwandura, agomba kwambara imyenda y'ubuvuzi ishobora gukoreshwa, kandi abakozi bo mu modoka bagomba kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi by'umuntu ku giti cye.
Inkweto n'ibindi bikoresho bikoreshwa birasabwa kujugunywa mu mufuka ufite ubukana bw'ibicurane, hanyuma aho byandujwe hagakorwa isuku no gukingirwa. Ku mato y'ubwato n'andi mato y'abagenzi, harimo n'amato y'ubucuruzi, kugenzura ibyago birimo gutinda urugendo mu gihe umuntu arwaye no kwishyirira mu kato mu gihe afite umuriro cyangwa indi ndwara mu gihe ari mu bwato no kumenyesha abaganga bo mu bwato byihuse.
Mu buryo bwiza, urwego rw'ubuvuzi rukenera gukurikirana mu cyumba cy'umuntu wahawe akato. CDC isaba ko amashuri n'ibigo byita ku bana bifungwa by'agateganyo kugira ngo haboneke isuku n'ubwisungane mu kwivuza, haba mu gihe umuntu wafashwe n'icyorezo aboneka mu muryango cyangwa mu gihe atagaragaye.
Aho hashobora kuba hari ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo ry'ubwandu buciriritse cyangwa ridakomeye, politiki yo gutandukanya abantu ishobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa, nko guhagarika ingendo zo mu mirima, guterana no kwigisha umubiri cyangwa ibindi bikorwa bikomeye birimo amasomo yo gusenga cyangwa gusangira mu mazu y'uburiro, kongera intera hagati y'amadesika, guhindura amasaha yo kuza no gusohoka, kugabanya abashyitsi badakenewe no gushyiraho ahantu hatandukanye ho kwita ku bana bafite ibimenyetso bisa n'iby'ibicurane.
Mu gihe hari ubwandu bukomeye mu baturage, amashuri ashobora gufungwa igihe kirekire, harimo n'ingamba zo kwirinda guhungabana. Abakozi b'inzego z'ubuyobozi bakora imirimo isanzwe, CDC ibona ko bafite ibyago bike by'ubuzima.
Abashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bagomba guhura n'abandi bantu banduye cyangwa bakekwaho kwandura COVID-19, basabwa gukurikiza amabwiriza y'uko bagomba kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bikwiye, kimwe n'abaganga b'ubutabazi.
Iyo hari umuntu wahuye cyane n'undi mu gihe cyo kwitabwaho, abakozi bagomba gusukura no gukaraba imyenda n'ibikoresho byabo bakoresheje umuti wo gusukura cyangwa umwanda mu rugo mbere yo kongera kubikoresha, kandi bagakurikiza gahunda zisanzwe zo gutwika PPE zakoreshejwe mu gihe gito, gutandukanya imyenda no kuyisukura.
OSHA yemeza ko hari abakozi bamwe na bamwe bo mu nzego z'ubuzima n'abakora mu mirimo y'ubuvuzi bafite ibyago byo kwandura cyangwa se by'ubukana.
Ibikorwa bifite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura birimo gutanga serivisi z'ubuzima, gutabara, gukora mu mavuriro no gutwara abarwayi mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi, cyangwa mu gihe umuntu yaba yarakoranye n'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho COVID-19.
Abarwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura niba abakozi bakora ibikorwa byo gukora aerosol cyangwa bakusanya cyangwa bagakora ibipimo ku barwayi nk'abo.
Uburyo bwo gukora aerosol burimo intubation, ubuvuzi bwo guteka, bronchoscopes, imiterere imwe n'imwe y'amenyo, no gusuzuma cyangwa gutoragura ingero.
Mu mirimo yo mu cyumba cy'ibariro irimo n'abakozi bakora mu gutegura imirambo y'abantu bapfuye bafite COVID-19 bizwi cyangwa bakekwaho; iyo bakoze autopsies, baba bafite ibyago byo kwandura. Muri ibi byiciro by'ibyago harimo ibyumba by'ubwirinzi by'ubwubatsi birimo no gukora imikorere yo gukora aerosol.
Mu bigo bimwe na bimwe by'ubuvuzi n'amazu y'imva, uburyo bwo guhumeka bufite ubukana bw'umuvuduko udakwiriye bushobora kuba bwiza.
Ibipimo bigomba gukoreshwa hakurikijwe ibipimo by'ubwirinzi bw'ibinyabuzima (Biosecurity Level 3).
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye ko abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakekwaho kuba barwaye, bakirindwa mu byumba by'abarwayi. Kimwe n'ibindi bikoresho bya PPE, OSHA yasabye ko abakozi bakora mu mirimo yo gukora aerosol bakoresha imashini zo guhumeka mu kirere, bakoreshwa mu gihe bari mu ntera ya metero 6 z'abarwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye SARS-CoV-2.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, masike yo mu bwoko bwa N95 yemewe na NIOSH cyangwa irenze, igomba gukoreshwa mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi, mu buryo bwanditse, harimo ibipimo by'imiterere, amahugurwa, n'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi.
Ubundi buryo bwo guhumeka bushobora gutanga uburinzi bwiza kandi bugatuma abakozi bumva bamerewe neza. WHO ntishishikariza abantu guhumeka umubiri wose, kuko COVID-19 ari indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, ntiyisakaza binyuze mu bindi bice by'umubiri.
OMS isaba ko abasirikare bakora ibizamini ku birometero byinshi gusa aribo bakoresha udupfukamunwa.
Ku bakozi bakusanya, bita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 barimo kuvurwa, cyangwa babatwara, badafite uburyo bwo gukora aerosol, WHO irasaba gukoresha udupfukamunwa, udupfukamunwa, n'utugati, bikoreshwa mu kubaga, mu kwambara indorerwamo cyangwa mu guhanagura mu maso.
Iyo habonetse uburyo bwo gukora aerosol, mu mwanya w'igitambaro cyo kumuhumeka, hakoreshwa N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko PPE itari ihagije ku isi, WHO irasaba ko hakoreshwa ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, nka Telemedicine, Windows zihumanye, kugirango abarwayi ba COVID-19 bagere mu byumba bakoresheje PPE gusa, bakoresha abarwayi bakoresha PPE gusa, WHO irasaba ko bakoresha masike imwe yo guhumeka, bakoresha masike imwe gusa mu gihe bakorera abarwayi benshi bafite icyorezo kimwe, bagenzura kandi bakagenzura urubuga rw'itangwa rya PPE, kandi bakoresha masike mu gihe batagira inkunga yo gukoresha masike.
