Twiringiye ko tuzakora amasaha agera kuri 4 ku munsi cyangwa amasaha 20 mu cyumweru kugeza igihe tuzabwirwa ikindi kintu.
Ntabwo turi gutangaza ko turi mu biruhuko - niba ushobora gukora amasaha menshi, ushobora gukoresha ubu buryo muri ubu bukangurambaga.
Ariko, isi muri iki gihe ntishobora kwitegereza, kandi waba ushaka kwita ku bo ukunda, gutwara ibicuruzwa cyangwa kujya kwa muganga, ubuzima bwawe ni bwo bw'ibanze.
Ntitujya dukurikirana igihe cyanyu.
Niba urwaye, ntugire akazi.
Si ngombwa ko tuvuga, ariko turabikora.
Nta kiruhuko cyo kurwara cyangwa PTO bikenewe - gusa ubwire umuyobozi wawe, ufashe itsinda ryawe guhindura kalendari n'ingengabihe, kugira ngo ujye ukora neza kugeza igihe imirimo ikomeye izaba yarangiye.
(Niba wafashwe na COVID-19, nyamuneka ubwire Brian muri T&C Ops, kugira ngo T&C izagushyigikire kandi ikore ibishoboka byose kugirango imikorere yawe ijyane n'ubuyobozi).
Abakozi bakora amasaha menshi bazahabwa umushahara wuzuye.
Twabivuze kandi turongera kubisubiramo, ku birebana no kubaha inshingano zacu ku bakoranabushake bacu ndetse n'abo dukorana bakora amasaha y'ikirenga.
Buri wese azajya ahembwa amasaha runaka bitewe n'akazi akora mu mimerere isanzwe.
Ibyo birimo no kurwara cyangwa kudashobora gukora.
Niba ushaka gukora, turagufasha.
Abantu benshi bakoresha akazi nk'uburyo bwo guhangana n'imihangayiko y'isi idukikije.
By'umwihariko mu bihe nk'ibi, ibyo dukora bishobora kugira inyungu zidasanzwe.
Byongeye kandi, ni ukwita kuri wowe ubwawe.
Icyo dusaba ni uko mwaganira n'abayobozi banyu, kugira ngo tumenye icyo twiteze, maze dushobore kugira ibyo duhindura.
Hari imirimo imwe n'imwe ifatwa nk'ibyangombwa.
Hari ibintu bimwe na bimwe tugomba gukomeza gukora.
SRE, HR Ops, Trust & Safety na Fundraising Team (mu zindi) ni zo zikora imirimo y'ingenzi, ishobora gukenera ubufasha bw'inyongera.
