Hari byinshi byo gukora kuri twese, reka twibande gusa ku mishinga ikomeye.
Gukora buhoro ubu, ntabwo bizatuma ubura amafaranga.
Nyuma y'iki gihuha cy'isi, ntabwo dufite gahunda yo gukora amasaha abiri kugira ngo turangize akazi.
Ntibazakwitega ko ukora amasaha y'ikirenga kugira ngo ukomeze gukora amasaha y'akazi asa n'aho adashoboka.
Twemeye ko ibintu byahindutse, kandi igihe bibaye ngombwa, tuzakora dushyiraho intego n'igihe ntarengwa bishya.
