Mu gihe dushyiraho ibyifuzo ku gihe gishya cy'akazi ka buri munsi kandi gihuje n'ukuri, intego yacu ni ugushyiraho igihe ntarengwa cyo gutanga gahunda y'umwaka wa 2020-2021.
Intego yacu ni ugutanga igitekerezo cyo kwagura gahunda yacu ya 2019-2020, kugirango abakozi babone umwanya munini wo gukora ingengo y'imari kugirango bashyire imbere imirimo yingenzi, kwita ku giti cyabo no kwita ku bandi bantu, bakeneye gukora mu byumweru bike biri imbere cyangwa bifuza gukora igihe gito.
Uko kongera igihe bizatuma umusaruro w'ibikorwa byo gutegura no guhangayika mu rwego rw'umuryango wose bigabanuka cyane.
Mu cyumweru gitaha tuzatanga igitekerezo cyacu imbere y'inama, kandi nitubimenya tuzatuma abahagarariye n'abakozi bacu bamenya uko tuzakomeza.
Ndashimira APP Team ku buyobozi bwayo muri ibi.
Mu by'ukuri, kugira ngo umuntu agire ubuzima bwiza, agomba kuba afite ibyangombwa by'ubushakashatsi.
Mu cyumweru gishize, twamenye ko umukozi wacu wo mu karere ka SF ashobora kuba yaranduye virusi ya COVID-19.
Nyamara, mu buryo bw'ubwitonzi, twashyizeho itsinda ry'abakora isuku yo kwirinda virusi kugira ngo basukure ibice byose by'ibiro byacu by'i San Francisco.
Bakoresha umuti urinda mikorobe wo mu rwego rwo hejuru ukoreshwa mu bitaro, kugira ngo bakureho indwara ku mpande zose, ndetse no mu byumba by'imbere n'ibiro by'inzu yacu.
Iyi nyubako ikoresha ingamba zayo bwite zo kwirinda, zikoresha ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bifasha abahatuye kurinda umutekano wabo.
Twishimira ko igihe tuzaba dufashe umwanzuro wo kugaruka, ayo ma biro azaba yiteguye gukora.
Ibiro byacu biri mu turere twa WeWork, aho twaganiriye n'abandi bakozi bo mu karere ka DC ku bijyanye n'uburyo bakemura COVID-19.
Mu cyumweru gishize, ibiro byacu bya DC byahindutse ahantu hatandukanye cyane hakurikijwe amabwiriza twasangiye na San Francisco.
Nk'uko bamwe mu bo dukorana mu karere ka New York bazi, turimo kuganira ku bijyanye no gukodesha ahantu i Brooklyn.
Ibi biganiro birimo gukorwa, ariko dushobora gutinda.
Bamwe mu bo dukorana barimo gukora kure ku nshuro ya mbere.
