Itsinda ry'abakozi mu by'imikorere ryita ku mikoreshereze y'imikorere y'abantu (HR) ririmo kureba ku 'Webinar-based Ergonomics' kugira ngo rifashe mu kongera imikorere y'imirimo itangwa mu rwego rw'umuryango.
Mu cyumweru gishize, twasabye abahawe inkunga y'umuryango bose guhagarika ibikorwa by'iterambere bitangwa na Wikimedia nka "Editathons" kugeza igihe OMS itangarije ko icyorezo kirangiye.
Twababwiye ko twumvise ko gusaba ko habaho guhagarika ibikorwa n'ibindi bibuza, byatuma tudashobora kugera ku gihe bemeranyijwe cyo gutanga inkunga, kandi ko nta muntu uzashyirwaho ibihano kubera gutinda cyangwa guhindura intego.
Mu cyumweru gitaha, tuzakomeza gukurikirana amabwiriza y'inyongera yatanzwe kuri Wikimedia n'andi materaniro y'akarere n'ay'amatorero.
Umwuka rusange w'umuryango mpuzamahanga wagize agahinda kubera ubwo buriganya ariko nanone ugaragaza ko hari ibyishimo biterwa no kugira umuco no kuba dushobora kwibanda ku muryango wacu, Wikimedia n'abandi.
Mu gihe kiri imbere, CRT irimo gukora ku gushyiraho page kuri Meta-Wiki kugira ngo itange umwanya ku baturage kugira ngo bagenzure ingaruka kandi bakurikirane itumanaho ryacu na bo.
