OMS yatangaje ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020 ko izina ry'ubuvuzi rizaba "COVID-19".
Umuyobozi wa OMS, Tendros Edhanom Ghebreyesus, yavuze ko CO ari coronavirus, VI ari virusi, D ari indwara, kandi 19 ni umwaka icyorezo cya mbere cyagaragaye i Lakshmi: 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Iryo zina ryahawe abantu kugira ngo birinde kuvuga ahantu runaka (urugero, u Bushinwa), inyamaswa, cyangwa itsinda ry'abantu, hakurikijwe amabwiriza mpuzamahanga yo kwita amazina, kandi hagamijwe kwirinda ko umuntu wese yabonwa nk'uwacengewe. Iyi virusi itera COVID-19 yitwa SARS-CoV-2.
Mu itumanaho rusange, WHO ikoresha "virusi ya COVID-19" na "virusi itera COVID-19".
Iyi ndwara na virusi byombi byitwa "coronavirus".
