Nubwo nta rukingo ruboneka, inzego zitandukanye zirimo gukora 'abashaka urukingo'.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere kuri SARS-CoV-2 burakoreshwa, kuko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha ingirabuzima fatizo ya ACE2 mu kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'umuntu.
Kugeza ubu, hatangijwe uburyo butatu bwo gukingira.
Icya mbere, abashakashatsi bifuza gukora urukingo rwa virusi.
