Ubundi buryo ni urukingo rw'ibanze, rugamije gukora urukingo rwica umubiri ku buryo rukora ku gice runaka cy'iyo virusi.
Ku bijyanye na SARS-CoV-2, ubushakashatsi bwibanze ku poroteyine ya S-spike ifasha virusi gutandukanya ingirabuzimafatizo ACE2 na neurons.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni urukingo rwa aside ya nukiliya (urukingo rwa ADN cyangwa RNA, ikoranabuhanga rishya mu gukora inkingo).
Muri ubwo buryo butatu, urukingo rw'igerageza rwagombye kugeragezwa kugira ngo rugere ku burenganzira n'umutekano. Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020, i Seattle hatangijwe igerageza ry'urukingo rwari rufite abantu bane b'abakorerabushake.
Uru rukingo rufite kode ya gakondo idahungabanya, ikorwa mu buryo bw'imiterere ya virusi ituma habaho iyi ndwara.
