Nitasoxanide yagaragajwe ko ari ingirakamaro mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi nyuma yo kugaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi buke bwo kugabanya ubukana bwayo. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko kubanza gukingira poroteyine ya spike mu buryo bwa TMPRSS2 ari ngombwa mu kwinjiza SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu guhuza na ACE-2 mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga.
