Iyo serum ferritin ihuriweho n'igenzura ry'amaraso kugira ngo hamenyekane cytoquin storm, bivuze ko kurwanya iterambere ry'iyo virusi, ryamaze kuba intandaro y'urupfu mu bantu bamwe na bamwe bayanduye.
